import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react';
import {
  View,
  Text,
  StyleSheet,
  ScrollView,
  TouchableOpacity,
  Alert,
  Dimensions,
  Platform,
  TextInput,
  Animated,
} from 'react-native';
import { useLocalSearchParams, router } from 'expo-router';
import { Ionicons } from '@expo/vector-icons';
import { useTheme } from '@/contexts/ThemeContext';
import { useAuth } from '@/contexts/AuthContext';
import { GoalsService, Goal } from '@/services/goalsService';
import { normalizeFont, spacing, wp, hp } from '@/utils/responsive';
import { getCurrencyByCode } from '@/utils/currencies';
import * as Haptics from 'expo-haptics';
import { LinearGradient } from 'expo-linear-gradient';
import { FluentEmoji } from '@/components/FluentEmoji';

const { width } = Dimensions.get('window');

export default function GoalDetailsScreen() {
  const { id } = useLocalSearchParams();
  const { colors, isDark } = useTheme();
  const { user } = useAuth();
  const [goal, setGoal] = useState<Goal | null>(null);
  const [loading, setLoading] = useState(true);
  const [showProgressInput, setShowProgressInput] = useState(false);
  const [progressAmount, setProgressAmount] = useState('');
  
  // Animation values
  const progressAnimation = useState(new Animated.Value(0))[0];
  const cardScale = useState(new Animated.Value(0.9))[0];
  const fadeIn = useState(new Animated.Value(0))[0];

  // Currency formatting function
  const formatCurrency = (amount: number) => {
    const userCurrency = user?.currency || 'INR';
    const currencyInfo = getCurrencyByCode(userCurrency);
    const symbol = currencyInfo?.symbol || 'Ã¢â€šÂ¹';
    
    // Format amount with proper locale and currency symbol
    return `${symbol}${Math.round(amount).toLocaleString('en-IN')}`;
  };

  useEffect(() => {
    if (id) {
      loadGoal();
    }
  }, [id]);

  useEffect(() => {
    if (goal) {
      // Animate progress bar
      Animated.timing(progressAnimation, {
        toValue: getProgressPercentage() / 100,
        duration: 1500,
        useNativeDriver: false,
      }).start();

      // Animate cards entrance
      Animated.parallel([
        Animated.timing(cardScale, {
          toValue: 1,
          duration: 600,
          useNativeDriver: true,
        }),
        Animated.timing(fadeIn, {
          toValue: 1,
          duration: 800,
          useNativeDriver: true,
        }),
      ]).start();
    }
  }, [goal]);

  const loadGoal = async () => {
    try {
      setLoading(true);
      const goalData = await GoalsService.getGoalById(id as string);
      setGoal(goalData);
    } catch (error) {
      console.error('Error loading goal:', error);
      Alert.alert('Error', 'Failed to load goal details');
    } finally {
      setLoading(false);
    }
  };

  const handleHaptic = () => {
    if (Platform.OS !== "web") {
      Haptics.impactAsync(Haptics.ImpactFeedbackStyle.Light);
    }
  };

  const navigateBack = () => {
    handleHaptic();
    router.back();
  };

  const updateProgress = async () => {
    if (!progressAmount.trim() || !goal) return;
    
    try {
      const amount = parseFloat(progressAmount);
      if (isNaN(amount) || amount <= 0) {
        Alert.alert('Invalid Amount', 'Please enter a valid positive number');
        return;
      }

      await GoalsService.updateProgress(goal.id, amount);
      
      // Reload the goal to show updated progress
      await loadGoal();
      
      // Reset form
      setProgressAmount('');
      setShowProgressInput(false);
      
      Alert.alert('Success', `Progress updated! Added $${amount.toFixed(2)} to your goal. Ã°Å¸Å½Â¯`);
    } catch (error) {
      console.error('Error updating progress:', error);
      Alert.alert('Error', 'Failed to update progress. Please try again.');
    }
  };

  const calculateSavings = () => {
    if (!goal) return null;
    
    // Parse dates more reliably by creating them in local timezone
    const today = new Date();
    const todayYear = today.getFullYear();
    const todayMonth = today.getMonth();
    const todayDay = today.getDate();
    
    // Create today at start of day in local timezone
    const todayStart = new Date(todayYear, todayMonth, todayDay);
    
    // Parse deadline date parts
    const deadlineParts = goal.deadline.split('-');
    const deadlineYear = parseInt(deadlineParts[0]);
    const deadlineMonth = parseInt(deadlineParts[1]) - 1; // Month is 0-indexed
    const deadlineDay = parseInt(deadlineParts[2]);
    
    // Create deadline at start of day in local timezone
    const deadlineStart = new Date(deadlineYear, deadlineMonth, deadlineDay);
    
    // Calculate days remaining
    const timeDiff = deadlineStart.getTime() - todayStart.getTime();
    const daysRemaining = Math.ceil(timeDiff / (1000 * 3600 * 24));
    
    if (daysRemaining <= 0) return null;
    
    // Calculate remaining amount needed
    const remainingAmount = goal.target_amount - goal.current_amount;
    
    // Calculate savings needed for remaining amount
    const dailySavings = remainingAmount / daysRemaining;
    
    // Calculate monthly savings more accurately
    // Use actual days in current month
    const daysInMonth = new Date(todayYear, todayMonth + 1, 0).getDate();
    const monthlySavings = dailySavings * daysInMonth;
    
    // Add debugging info
    console.log('Savings calculation:', {
      target: goal.target_amount,
      current: goal.current_amount,
      remaining: remainingAmount,
      deadline: goal.deadline,
      deadlineDate: deadlineStart.toISOString(),
      today: todayStart.toISOString(),
      daysRemaining,
      dailySavings,
      daysInMonth,
      monthlySavings
    });
    
    return {
      daysRemaining,
      dailySavings,
      monthlySavings,
      remainingAmount
    };
  };

  const formatDate = (dateString: string) => {
    const date = new Date(dateString);
    return date.toLocaleDateString('en-US', {
      year: 'numeric',
      month: 'long',
      day: 'numeric'
    });
  };

  const getProgressPercentage = () => {
    if (!goal) return 0;
    return Math.min((goal.current_amount / goal.target_amount) * 100, 100);
  };

  const getProgressColor = () => {
    const percentage = getProgressPercentage();
    if (percentage >= 80) return '#4ECDC4'; // Green
    if (percentage >= 50) return '#FFD93D'; // Yellow
    return '#FF6B6B'; // Red
  };

  const getContrastTextColor = (backgroundColor: string) => {
    // Convert hex to RGB
    const hex = backgroundColor.replace('#', '');
    const r = parseInt(hex.substr(0, 2), 16);
    const g = parseInt(hex.substr(2, 2), 16);
    const b = parseInt(hex.substr(4, 2), 16);
    
    // Calculate luminance
    const luminance = (0.299 * r + 0.587 * g + 0.114 * b) / 255;
    
    // Return black for light backgrounds, white for dark backgrounds
    return luminance > 0.5 ? '#000000' : '#FFFFFF';
  };



  if (loading) {
    return (
      <View style={[styles.container, { backgroundColor: colors.background }]}>
        <View style={styles.loadingContainer}>
          <FluentEmoji emoji="Ã°Å¸Å½Â¯" size={60} />
          <Text style={[styles.loadingText, { color: colors.text }]}>Loading your goal...</Text>
        </View>
      </View>
    );
  }

  if (!goal) {
    return (
      <View style={[styles.container, { backgroundColor: colors.background }]}>
        <View style={styles.errorContainer}>
          <FluentEmoji emoji="Ã°Å¸Ëœâ€¢" size={60} />
          <Text style={[styles.errorText, { color: colors.text }]}>Goal not found</Text>
          <TouchableOpacity style={[styles.backButton, { backgroundColor: colors.primary }]} onPress={navigateBack}>
            <Text style={[styles.backButtonText, { color: '#FFFFFF' }]}>Go Back</Text>
          </TouchableOpacity>
        </View>
      </View>
    );
  }

  const savings = calculateSavings();

  return (
    <View style={[styles.container, { backgroundColor: colors.background }]}>
      {/* Header */}
      <View style={styles.header}>
        <TouchableOpacity onPress={navigateBack} style={styles.backButton}>
          <Ionicons name="arrow-back" size={24} color={colors.text} />
        </TouchableOpacity>
        <Text style={[styles.headerTitle, { color: colors.text }]}>Goal Details</Text>
        <View style={styles.placeholder} />
      </View>

      <ScrollView style={styles.content} showsVerticalScrollIndicator={false}>
        {/* Hero Goal Card */}
        <Animated.View 
          style={[
            styles.heroCard, 
            { 
              backgroundColor: goal.color ? (isDark ? goal.color + 'DD' : goal.color) : (isDark ? '#8BC34A' : '#A2E57B'),
              transform: [{ scale: cardScale }],
              opacity: fadeIn,
            }
          ]}
        >
          <View style={styles.heroContent}>
            <View style={styles.heroLeft}>
              <View style={styles.heroInfo}>
                <View style={styles.heroTitleRow}>
                  <View style={[styles.heroEmojiContainer, { backgroundColor: 'rgba(255,255,255,0.2)' }]}>
                    <FluentEmoji emoji={goal.emoji || 'Ã°Å¸Å½Â¯'} size={28} />
                  </View>
                  <Text style={[styles.heroTitle, { color: '#FFFFFF' }]}>{goal.title}</Text>
                </View>
                <Text style={[styles.heroCategory, { color: '#FFFFFF' }]}>{goal.category}</Text>
              </View>
            </View>
            <View style={styles.heroRight}>
              <Text style={[styles.heroAmount, { color: '#FFFFFF' }]}>
                {formatCurrency(goal.current_amount || 0)}
              </Text>
              <Text style={[styles.heroTarget, { color: '#FFFFFF' }]}>
                of {formatCurrency(goal.target_amount)}
              </Text>
            </View>
          </View>
        </Animated.View>

        {/* Progress Card */}
        <Animated.View 
          style={[
            styles.progressCard, 
            { 
              backgroundColor: colors.surface,
              transform: [{ scale: cardScale }],
              opacity: fadeIn,
            }
          ]}
        >
          <View style={styles.progressHeader}>
            <Text style={[styles.progressLabel, { color: colors.text }]}>Progress</Text>
            <Text style={[styles.progressPercentage, { color: '#FFFFFF' }]}>
              {getProgressPercentage().toFixed(1)}%
            </Text>
          </View>
          
          <View style={[styles.progressBarContainer, { backgroundColor: colors.border }]}>
            <Animated.View 
              style={[
                styles.progressFill, 
                { 
                  width: progressAnimation.interpolate({
                    inputRange: [0, 1],
                    outputRange: ['0%', '100%'],
                  }),
                  backgroundColor: getProgressColor()
                }
              ]} 
            />
          </View>
          
          <View style={styles.progressStats}>
            <View style={styles.progressStat}>
              <Text style={[styles.progressStatLabel, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>Current</Text>
              <Text style={[styles.progressStatValue, { color: colors.text }]}>
                ${goal.current_amount?.toFixed(2) || '0.00'}
              </Text>
            </View>
            <View style={styles.progressStat}>
              <Text style={[styles.progressStatLabel, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>Target</Text>
              <Text style={[styles.progressStatValue, { color: colors.text }]}>
                ${goal.target_amount.toFixed(2)}
              </Text>
            </View>
            <View style={styles.progressStat}>
              <Text style={[styles.progressStatLabel, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>Remaining</Text>
              <Text style={[styles.progressStatValue, { color: isDark ? '#90EE90' : '#2E7D32' }]}>
                ${(goal.target_amount - (goal.current_amount || 0)).toFixed(2)}
              </Text>
            </View>
          </View>
        </Animated.View>

        {/* Goal Details Card */}
        <Animated.View 
          style={[
            styles.detailsCard, 
            { 
              backgroundColor: colors.surface,
              transform: [{ scale: cardScale }],
              opacity: fadeIn,
            }
          ]}
        >
          <View style={styles.detailsHeader}>
            <Text style={[styles.detailsTitle, { color: colors.text }]}>Goal Information</Text>
          </View>
          
          <View style={styles.detailsContent}>
            <View style={[styles.detailRow, { borderBottomColor: colors.border }]}>
              <Text style={[styles.detailLabel, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>Deadline</Text>
              <Text style={[styles.detailValue, { color: colors.text }]}>
                {formatDate(goal.deadline)}
              </Text>
            </View>
            
            <View style={[styles.detailRow, { borderBottomColor: colors.border }]}>
              <Text style={[styles.detailLabel, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>Status</Text>
                              <View style={[
                  styles.statusBadge, 
                  { 
                    backgroundColor: goal.completed ? '#4ECDC4' : '#90EE9020',
                    borderColor: goal.completed ? '#4ECDC4' : '#90EE90',
                  }
                ]}>
                  <Text style={[
                    styles.statusText, 
                    { color: goal.completed ? '#FFFFFF' : (isDark ? '#90EE90' : '#2E7D32') }
                  ]}>
                    {goal.completed ? 'Completed' : 'In Progress'}
                  </Text>
                </View>
            </View>
            
            <View style={[styles.detailRow, { borderBottomWidth: 0 }]}>
              <Text style={[styles.detailLabel, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>Color</Text>
              <View style={styles.colorPreview}>
                <View style={[styles.colorCircle, { backgroundColor: goal.color || '#A2E57B' }]} />
              </View>
            </View>
          </View>
        </Animated.View>

        {/* Savings Calculator Card */}
        {savings && (
          <Animated.View 
            style={[
              styles.savingsCard, 
              { 
                backgroundColor: colors.surface,
                transform: [{ scale: cardScale }],
                opacity: fadeIn,
              }
            ]}
          >
            <View style={styles.savingsHeader}>
              <Text style={[styles.savingsTitle, { color: colors.text }]}>
                Smart Savings Plan
              </Text>
            </View>
            
            {/* Remaining Amount Highlight */}
            <View style={[styles.remainingAmountSection, { backgroundColor: '#90EE9015' }]}>
              <Text style={[styles.remainingAmountLabel, { color: isDark ? '#90EE90' : '#2E7D32' }]}>
                Still need to save
              </Text>
              <Text style={[styles.remainingAmountValue, { color: isDark ? '#90EE90' : '#2E7D32' }]}>
                {formatCurrency(savings.remainingAmount)}
              </Text>
            </View>
            
            {/* Savings Breakdown */}
            <View style={styles.savingsBreakdown}>
              <View style={styles.savingsItem}>
                <View style={[styles.savingsIcon, { backgroundColor: colors.primary + '20' }]}>
                  <FluentEmoji emoji="Ã°Å¸â€œâ€¦" size={24} />
                </View>
                <View style={styles.savingsItemContent}>
                  <Text style={[styles.savingsItemLabel, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>
                    Days Left
                  </Text>
                  <Text style={[styles.savingsItemValue, { color: colors.text }]}>
                    {savings.daysRemaining}
                  </Text>
                </View>
              </View>
              
              <View style={styles.savingsItem}>
                <View style={[styles.savingsIcon, { backgroundColor: '#FF6B6B20' }]}>
                  <FluentEmoji emoji="Ã°Å¸â€™Â°" size={24} />
                </View>
                <View style={styles.savingsItemContent}>
                  <Text style={[styles.savingsItemLabel, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>
                    Daily Target
                  </Text>
                  <Text style={[styles.savingsItemValue, { color: colors.text }]}>
                    {formatCurrency(savings.dailySavings)}
                  </Text>
                </View>
              </View>
              
              {/* Only show monthly target if deadline is 30+ days away */}
              {savings.daysRemaining >= 30 && (
                <View style={styles.savingsItem}>
                  <View style={[styles.savingsIcon, { backgroundColor: '#4ECDC4' }]}>
                    <FluentEmoji emoji="Ã°Å¸â€œÅ " size={24} />
                  </View>
                  <View style={styles.savingsItemContent}>
                    <Text style={[styles.savingsItemLabel, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>
                      Monthly Target
                    </Text>
                    <Text style={[styles.savingsItemValue, { color: colors.text }]}>
                      {formatCurrency(savings.monthlySavings)}
                    </Text>
                  </View>
                </View>
              )}
            </View>
            
            <View style={[styles.savingsNote, { backgroundColor: colors.background }]}>
              <Text style={[styles.savingsNoteText, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>
                Save this amount regularly to reach your goal on time! 
              </Text>
            </View>
          </Animated.View>
        )}

        {/* Action Button */}
        <Animated.View 
          style={[
            styles.actionButtonContainer,
            { 
              transform: [{ scale: cardScale }],
              opacity: fadeIn,
            }
          ]}
        >
          <TouchableOpacity 
            style={[styles.actionButton, { backgroundColor: colors.primary }]}
            onPress={() => {
              setShowProgressInput(true);
              handleHaptic();
            }}
          >
            <LinearGradient
              colors={[colors.primary, colors.primary + 'DD']}
              style={styles.actionButtonGradient}
            >
              <Text style={styles.actionButtonText}>Update Progress</Text>
            </LinearGradient>
          </TouchableOpacity>
        </Animated.View>
      </ScrollView>

      {/* Progress Input Modal */}
      {showProgressInput && (
        <View style={styles.modalOverlay}>
          <Animated.View 
            style={[
              styles.modalContent, 
              { backgroundColor: colors.surface },
              { transform: [{ scale: cardScale }] }
            ]}
          >
            <View style={styles.modalHeader}>
              <FluentEmoji emoji="Ã°Å¸Å½Â¯" size={32} />
              <Text style={[styles.modalTitle, { color: colors.text }]}>Update Progress</Text>
            </View>
            
            <Text style={[styles.modalSubtitle, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>
              How much did you save towards "{goal?.title}"?
            </Text>
            
            <TextInput
              style={[styles.progressInput, { 
                backgroundColor: colors.background,
                borderColor: colors.border,
                color: colors.text
              }]}
              placeholder="0.00"
              placeholderTextColor={colors.textSecondary}
              value={progressAmount}
              onChangeText={setProgressAmount}
              keyboardType="numeric"
              autoFocus
            />
            
            <View style={styles.modalButtons}>
              <TouchableOpacity 
                style={[styles.cancelButton, { backgroundColor: colors.border }]}
                onPress={() => {
                  setShowProgressInput(false);
                  setProgressAmount('');
                }}
              >
                <Text style={[styles.cancelButtonText, { color: colors.text }]}>Cancel</Text>
              </TouchableOpacity>
              <TouchableOpacity 
                style={[styles.saveButton, { backgroundColor: colors.primary }]}
                onPress={updateProgress}
              >
                <LinearGradient
                  colors={[colors.primary, colors.primary + 'DD']}
                  style={styles.saveButtonGradient}
                >
                  <Text style={[styles.saveButtonText, { color: '#FFFFFF' }]}>Update</Text>
                </LinearGradient>
              </TouchableOpacity>
            </View>
          </Animated.View>
        </View>
      )}
    </View>
  );
}

FILE: components/AddGoalBottomSheet.tsx

import React, { useMemo, useRef, useState } from 'react';
import {
  View,
  Text,
  StyleSheet,
  TouchableOpacity,
  TextInput,
  Alert,
  Platform,
  Modal,
  FlatList,
} from 'react-native';
import { Ionicons } from '@expo/vector-icons';
import { useTheme } from '@/contexts/ThemeContext';
import { useAuth } from '@/contexts/AuthContext';
import { GoalsService, CreateGoalData } from '@/services/goalsService';
import { FluentEmoji } from '@/components/FluentEmoji';
import { normalizeFont, spacing } from '@/utils/responsive';
import { getCurrencyByCode } from '@/utils/currencies';
import * as Haptics from 'expo-haptics';
import BottomSheet, { BottomSheetView, BottomSheetScrollView, BottomSheetBackdrop } from '@gorhom/bottom-sheet';
import DateTimePicker from '@react-native-community/datetimepicker';
import expenseDetector from '@/services/expenseDetector';

interface AddGoalBottomSheetProps {
  isVisible: boolean;
  onClose: () => void;
  onGoalCreated: () => void;
}

export const AddGoalBottomSheet: React.FC<AddGoalBottomSheetProps> = ({
  isVisible,
  onClose,
  onGoalCreated,
}) => {
  const { colors } = useTheme();
  const { user } = useAuth();
  const [loading, setLoading] = useState(false);
  const [title, setTitle] = useState('');
  const [targetAmount, setTargetAmount] = useState('');
  const [deadline, setDeadline] = useState(new Date());
  const [showDatePicker, setShowDatePicker] = useState(false);
  const [category, setCategory] = useState('');
  const [selectedColor, setSelectedColor] = useState('#A2E57B');
  const [showCategoryPicker, setShowCategoryPicker] = useState(false);

  // Get available categories from expense detector
  const availableCategories = useMemo(() => expenseDetector.getCategories(), []);

  // Bottom sheet ref and snap points
  const bottomSheetRef = useRef<BottomSheet>(null);
  const snapPoints = useMemo(() => ['90%'], []);

  // Goal colors
  const goalColors = [
    "#A2E57B", "#AEE9F9", "#F9B7DD", "#FFD93D", 
    "#FF6B6B", "#4ECDC4", "#45B7D1", "#96CEB4"
  ];

  // Load data when bottom sheet becomes visible
  React.useEffect(() => {
    if (isVisible) {
      bottomSheetRef.current?.snapToIndex(0);
    }
  }, [isVisible]);

  const handleClose = () => {
    Haptics.impactAsync(Haptics.ImpactFeedbackStyle.Light);
    onClose();
  };

  const handleDateChange = (event: any, selectedDate?: Date) => {
    setShowDatePicker(Platform.OS === 'ios');
    if (selectedDate) {
      setDeadline(selectedDate);
    }
  };

  const showDatePickerModal = () => {
    setShowDatePicker(true);
    Haptics.impactAsync(Haptics.ImpactFeedbackStyle.Light);
  };

  const formatDate = (date: Date) => {
    return date.toLocaleDateString('en-US', {
      year: 'numeric',
      month: 'short',
      day: 'numeric'
    });
  };



  const handleCreateGoal = async () => {
    if (!title.trim() || !targetAmount.trim() || !category.trim()) {
      Alert.alert('Missing Information', 'Please fill in all required fields');
      return;
    }

    try {
      setLoading(true);
      Haptics.impactAsync(Haptics.ImpactFeedbackStyle.Medium);

      // Get the emoji for the selected category
      const selectedCategoryData = availableCategories.find(cat => cat.name === category.trim());
      const categoryEmoji = selectedCategoryData?.icon || 'Ã°Å¸Å½Â¯';

      const goalData: CreateGoalData = {
        title: title.trim(),
        target_amount: parseFloat(targetAmount),
        deadline: deadline.toISOString().split('T')[0], // Format as YYYY-MM-DD
        category: category.trim(),
        emoji: categoryEmoji,
        color: selectedColor,
      };

      await GoalsService.createGoal(goalData);
      
      // Reset form
      setTitle('');
      setTargetAmount('');
      setDeadline(new Date());
      setCategory('');
      setSelectedColor('#A2E57B');
      
      // Close and refresh
      onGoalCreated();
      onClose();
      
      Alert.alert('Success', 'Goal created successfully! Ã°Å¸Å½Â¯');
    } catch (error) {
      console.error('Error creating goal:', error);
      Alert.alert('Error', 'Failed to create goal. Please try again.');
    } finally {
      setLoading(false);
    }
  };

  if (!isVisible) return null;

  return (
    <>
              <BottomSheet
          ref={bottomSheetRef}
          index={0}
          snapPoints={snapPoints}
          enablePanDownToClose
          onClose={handleClose}
          backgroundStyle={[styles.bottomSheetBackground, { backgroundColor: colors.background }]}
          handleIndicatorStyle={[styles.handleIndicator, { backgroundColor: colors.border }]}
          backdropComponent={(props) => (
            <BottomSheetBackdrop
              {...props}
              disappearsOnIndex={-1}
              appearsOnIndex={0}
              pressBehavior="close"
              opacity={0.8}
            />
          )}
        >
        <BottomSheetView style={styles.container}>
          {/* Header */}
          <View style={styles.header}>
            <Text style={[styles.headerTitle, { color: colors.text }]}>Add New Goal</Text>
            <TouchableOpacity onPress={handleClose} style={styles.closeButton}>
              <Ionicons name="close" size={24} color={colors.text} />
            </TouchableOpacity>
          </View>

          <BottomSheetScrollView style={styles.content} showsVerticalScrollIndicator={false}>
            {/* Goal Title */}
            <View style={styles.inputGroup}>
              <Text style={[styles.label, { color: colors.text }]}>Goal Title</Text>
              <TextInput
                style={[styles.input, { 
                  backgroundColor: colors.surface,
                  borderColor: colors.border,
                  color: colors.text
                }]}
                placeholder="e.g., Emergency Fund, Vacation, New Car"
                placeholderTextColor={colors.textSecondary}
                value={title}
                onChangeText={setTitle}
              />
            </View>

            {/* Target Amount */}
            <View style={styles.inputGroup}>
              <Text style={[styles.label, { color: colors.text }]}>
                Target Amount ({(() => {
                  const userCurrency = user?.currency || 'INR';
                  const currencyInfo = getCurrencyByCode(userCurrency);
                  return currencyInfo?.symbol || 'Ã¢â€šÂ¹';
                })()})
              </Text>
              <TextInput
                style={[styles.input, { 
                  backgroundColor: colors.surface,
                  borderColor: colors.border,
                  color: colors.text
                }]}
                placeholder="0.00"
                placeholderTextColor={colors.textSecondary}
                value={targetAmount}
                onChangeText={setTargetAmount}
                keyboardType="numeric"
              />
            </View>

            {/* Category */}
            <View style={styles.inputGroup}>
              <Text style={[styles.label, { color: colors.text }]}>Category</Text>
              <TouchableOpacity
                style={[styles.categoryPickerButton, { 
                  backgroundColor: colors.surface,
                  borderColor: colors.border
                }]}
                onPress={() => setShowCategoryPicker(true)}
              >
                <Text style={[
                  styles.categoryPickerText, 
                  { color: category ? colors.text : colors.textSecondary }
                ]}>
                  {category || 'Select a category'}
                </Text>
                <Ionicons name="chevron-down" size={20} color={colors.textSecondary} />
              </TouchableOpacity>
            </View>

            {/* Deadline */}
            <View style={styles.inputGroup}>
              <Text style={[styles.label, { color: colors.text }]}>Deadline</Text>
              <TouchableOpacity
                style={[styles.datePickerButton, { 
                  backgroundColor: colors.surface,
                  borderColor: colors.border
                }]}
                onPress={showDatePickerModal}
              >
                <Text style={[styles.datePickerText, { color: colors.text }]}>
                  {formatDate(deadline)}
                </Text>
                <Ionicons name="calendar" size={20} color={colors.textSecondary} />
              </TouchableOpacity>
            </View>

            {/* Color Picker */}
            <View style={styles.inputGroup}>
              <Text style={[styles.label, { color: colors.text }]}>Choose Color</Text>
              <View style={styles.colorPicker}>
                {goalColors.map((color) => (
                  <TouchableOpacity
                    key={color}
                    style={[
                      styles.colorOption,
                      { backgroundColor: color },
                      selectedColor === color && styles.selectedColor
                    ]}
                    onPress={() => setSelectedColor(color)}
                  />
                ))}
              </View>
            </View>



            {/* Create Button */}
            <TouchableOpacity
              style={[
                styles.createButton,
                { backgroundColor: colors.primary },
                loading && { opacity: 0.7 }
              ]}
              onPress={handleCreateGoal}
              disabled={loading}
            >
              {loading ? (
                <Ionicons name="refresh" size={20} color="#FFFFFF" />
              ) : (
                <Ionicons name="checkmark" size={20} color="#FFFFFF" />
              )}
              <Text style={styles.createButtonText}>
                {loading ? 'Creating...' : 'Create Goal'}
              </Text>
            </TouchableOpacity>
          </BottomSheetScrollView>
        </BottomSheetView>
      </BottomSheet>

      {/* Date Picker Modal */}
      {showDatePicker && (
        <DateTimePicker
          value={deadline}
          mode="date"
          display={Platform.OS === 'ios' ? 'spinner' : 'default'}
          onChange={handleDateChange}
          minimumDate={new Date()}
        />
      )}

      {/* Category Picker Modal */}
      <Modal
        visible={showCategoryPicker}
        transparent={true}
        animationType="slide"
        onRequestClose={() => setShowCategoryPicker(false)}
      >
        <View style={styles.modalOverlay}>
          <View style={[styles.modalContent, { backgroundColor: colors.background }]}>
            <View style={[styles.modalHeader, { borderBottomColor: colors.border }]}>
              <Text style={[styles.modalTitle, { color: colors.text }]}>Select Category</Text>
              <TouchableOpacity
                onPress={() => setShowCategoryPicker(false)}
                style={styles.modalCloseButton}
              >
                <Ionicons name="close" size={24} color={colors.text} />
              </TouchableOpacity>
            </View>
            
            <FlatList
              data={availableCategories}
              keyExtractor={(item) => item.name}
              renderItem={({ item }) => (
                <TouchableOpacity
                  style={[
                    styles.categoryOption,
                    { borderBottomColor: colors.border }
                  ]}
                  onPress={() => {
                    setCategory(item.name);
                    setShowCategoryPicker(false);
                    Haptics.impactAsync(Haptics.ImpactFeedbackStyle.Light);
                  }}
                >
                  <View style={styles.categoryOptionContent}>
                    <FluentEmoji emoji={item.icon} size={24} />
                    <Text style={[styles.categoryName, { color: colors.text }]}>
                      {item.name}
                    </Text>
                  </View>
                  <Ionicons 
                    name="chevron-forward" 
                    size={20} 
                    color={colors.textSecondary} 
                  />
                </TouchableOpacity>
              )}
              showsVerticalScrollIndicator={false}
            />
          </View>
        </View>
      </Modal>
    </>
  );
};

const styles = StyleSheet.create({

FILE: components/AuthWrapper.tsx

import React from 'react';
import { View, Text, StyleSheet } from 'react-native';
import { useAuth } from '../contexts/AuthContext';
import { AuthScreen } from './AuthScreen';
import { useTheme } from '../contexts/ThemeContext';
import { LumaSpin } from './LumaSpin';

interface AuthWrapperProps {
  children: React.ReactNode;
}

export const AuthWrapper: React.FC<AuthWrapperProps> = ({ children }) => {
  const { user, loading } = useAuth();
  const { colors } = useTheme();
  const [loadingTimeout, setLoadingTimeout] = React.useState(false);

  React.useEffect(() => {
    // Add a timeout to prevent infinite loading
    const timeout = setTimeout(() => {
      if (loading) {
        console.log('âš ï¸ Auth loading timeout reached, forcing continue...');
        setLoadingTimeout(true);
      }
    }, 30000); // 30 seconds timeout

    return () => clearTimeout(timeout);
  }, [loading]);

  console.log('ðŸ” AuthWrapper - user:', user ? user.name : 'null', 'loading:', loading, 'timeout:', loadingTimeout);

  // Show loading screen while checking authentication
  if (loading && !loadingTimeout) {
    console.log('â³ AuthWrapper - showing loading state');
    return (
      <View style={[styles.loadingContainer, { backgroundColor: colors.background }]}>
        <LumaSpin variant="large" color={colors.primary} />
        <Text style={[styles.loadingText, { color: colors.text }]}>
          Loading your learning progress...
        </Text>
      </View>
    );
  }

  // If no user is authenticated, show the auth screen
  if (!user) {
    console.log('ðŸ”‘ AuthWrapper - showing auth screen');
    return <AuthScreen />;
  }

  // If user is authenticated, show the main app
  console.log('âœ… AuthWrapper - showing main app');
  return <>{children}</>;
};

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
  loadingContainer: {
    flex: 1,
    justifyContent: 'center',
    alignItems: 'center',
  },
  loadingText: {
    marginTop: 16,
    fontSize: 16,
    fontFamily: 'Parkinsans-Regular',
  },
});

FILE: components/ChangeGoalBottomSheet.tsx

import React, { useMemo, useRef, useState, useEffect } from 'react';
import {
  View,
  Text,
  StyleSheet,
  TouchableOpacity,
  FlatList,
  Alert,
} from 'react-native';
import { Ionicons } from '@expo/vector-icons';
import { useTheme } from '@/contexts/ThemeContext';
import { useAuth } from '@/contexts/AuthContext';
import { GoalsService, Goal } from '@/services/goalsService';
import { FluentEmoji } from '@/components/FluentEmoji';
import { normalizeFont, spacing, fontSize } from '@/utils/responsive';
import * as Haptics from 'expo-haptics';
import BottomSheet, { BottomSheetView, BottomSheetFlatList, BottomSheetBackdrop } from '@gorhom/bottom-sheet';

interface ChangeGoalBottomSheetProps {
  isVisible: boolean;
  onClose: () => void;
  onGoalChanged: (goal: Goal) => void;
  currentGoalId?: string;
}

export const ChangeGoalBottomSheet: React.FC<ChangeGoalBottomSheetProps> = ({
  isVisible,
  onClose,
  onGoalChanged,
  currentGoalId,
}) => {
  const { colors } = useTheme();
  const { user } = useAuth();
  const [loading, setLoading] = useState(false);
  const [goals, setGoals] = useState<Goal[]>([]);

  // Bottom sheet ref and snap points
  const bottomSheetRef = useRef<BottomSheet>(null);
  const snapPoints = useMemo(() => ['50%', '75%'], []);

  // Load goals when component mounts
  useEffect(() => {
    if (isVisible) {
      loadGoals();
    }
  }, [isVisible]);

  // Load goals when bottom sheet becomes visible
  useEffect(() => {
    if (isVisible) {
      bottomSheetRef.current?.snapToIndex(0);
    }
  }, [isVisible]);

  const loadGoals = async () => {
    try {
      setLoading(true);
      const goalsData = await GoalsService.getGoals();
      setGoals(goalsData);
    } catch (error) {
      console.error('Error loading goals:', error);
      Alert.alert('Error', 'Failed to load goals');
    } finally {
      setLoading(false);
    }
  };

  const handleClose = () => {
    Haptics.impactAsync(Haptics.ImpactFeedbackStyle.Light);
    onClose();
  };

  const handleGoalSelect = (goal: Goal) => {
    Haptics.impactAsync(Haptics.ImpactFeedbackStyle.Medium);
    onGoalChanged(goal);
    onClose();
  };

  const renderGoalItem = ({ item }: { item: Goal }) => {
    const isCurrentGoal = item.id === currentGoalId;
    const isCompleted = item.completed;
    
    return (
      <TouchableOpacity
        style={[
          styles.goalItem,
          { 
            backgroundColor: colors.surface,
            borderColor: isCurrentGoal ? colors.primary : colors.border,
            borderWidth: isCurrentGoal ? 2 : 1,
          }
        ]}
        onPress={() => handleGoalSelect(item)}
        activeOpacity={0.7}
      >
        <View style={styles.goalHeader}>
          <View style={styles.goalEmojiContainer}>
            <FluentEmoji emoji={item.emoji} size={24} />
          </View>
          
          <View style={styles.goalInfo}>
            <Text style={[styles.goalTitle, { color: colors.text }]} numberOfLines={1}>
              {item.title}
            </Text>
            <Text style={[styles.goalCategory, { color: colors.textSecondary }]} numberOfLines={1}>
              {item.category}
            </Text>
          </View>
          
          {isCurrentGoal && (
            <View style={styles.currentIndicator}>
              <Ionicons name="checkmark-circle" size={20} color={colors.primary} />
            </View>
          )}
          
          {isCompleted && (
            <View style={styles.completedIndicator}>
              <Ionicons name="trophy" size={20} color="#FFD700" />
            </View>
          )}
        </View>
        
        <View style={styles.goalProgress}>
          <View style={[styles.progressBar, { backgroundColor: colors.border }]}>
            <View 
              style={[
                styles.progressFill, 
                { 
                  backgroundColor: item.color || colors.primary,
                  width: `${Math.min((item.current_amount / item.target_amount) * 100, 100)}%`
                }
              ]} 
            />
          </View>
          
          <Text style={[styles.progressText, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>
            {item.current_amount.toLocaleString()} / {item.target_amount.toLocaleString()}
          </Text>
        </View>
      </TouchableOpacity>
    );
  };

  const renderHeader = () => (
    <View style={styles.header}>
      <Text style={[styles.headerTitle, { color: colors.text }]}>
        Change Learning Goal
      </Text>
      <Text style={[styles.headerSubtitle, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>
        Select a goal to focus on
      </Text>
      
      <TouchableOpacity style={styles.closeButton} onPress={handleClose}>
        <Ionicons name="close" size={24} color={colors.text} />
      </TouchableOpacity>
    </View>
  );

  const renderEmptyState = () => (
    <View style={styles.emptyState}>
      <FluentEmoji emoji="Ã°Å¸Å½Â¯" size={48} />
      <Text style={[styles.emptyStateTitle, { color: colors.text }]}>
        No Goals Yet
      </Text>
      <Text style={[styles.emptyStateText, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>
        Create your first learning goal to get started
      </Text>
    </View>
  );

  return (
    <BottomSheet
      ref={bottomSheetRef}
      index={isVisible ? 0 : -1}
      snapPoints={snapPoints}
      enablePanDownToClose={true}
      backgroundStyle={{ backgroundColor: colors.background }}
      handleIndicatorStyle={{ backgroundColor: colors.border }}
      onClose={handleClose}
      style={styles.bottomSheet}
      backdropComponent={(props) => (
        <BottomSheetBackdrop
          {...props}
          disappearsOnIndex={-1}
          appearsOnIndex={0}
          opacity={0.8}
        />
      )}
    >
      <BottomSheetView style={styles.container}>
        {renderHeader()}
        
        {loading ? (
          <View style={styles.loadingContainer}>
            <Text style={[styles.loadingText, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>
              Loading goals...
            </Text>
          </View>
        ) : goals.length === 0 ? (
          renderEmptyState()
        ) : (
          <BottomSheetFlatList
            data={goals}
            renderItem={renderGoalItem}
            keyExtractor={(item) => item.id}
            contentContainerStyle={styles.goalsList}
            showsVerticalScrollIndicator={false}
            ItemSeparatorComponent={() => <View style={styles.separator} />}
          />
        )}
      </BottomSheetView>
    </BottomSheet>
  );
};

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
  bottomSheet: {
    borderTopLeftRadius: 24,
    borderTopRightRadius: 24,
  },
  container: {
    flex: 1,
  },
  header: {
    paddingHorizontal: spacing.lg,
    paddingTop: spacing.lg,
    paddingBottom: spacing.md,
    borderBottomWidth: 1,
    borderBottomColor: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.1)',
  },
  headerTitle: {
    fontSize: fontSize.xl,
    fontFamily: 'Parkinsans-Bold',
    marginBottom: spacing.xs,
  },
  headerSubtitle: {
    fontSize: fontSize.md,
    fontFamily: 'Parkinsans-Regular',
    marginBottom: spacing.md,
  },
  closeButton: {
    position: 'absolute',
    top: spacing.lg,
    right: spacing.lg,
    padding: spacing.xs,
  },
  goalsList: {
    paddingHorizontal: spacing.lg,
    paddingBottom: spacing.xl,
  },
  goalItem: {
    padding: spacing.md,
    borderRadius: 16,
    marginVertical: spacing.xs,
    shadowColor: '#000',
    shadowOffset: { width: 0, height: 2 },
    shadowOpacity: 0.1,
    shadowRadius: 4,
    elevation: 2,
  },
  goalHeader: {
    flexDirection: 'row',
    alignItems: 'center',
    marginBottom: spacing.sm,
  },
  goalEmojiContainer: {
    marginRight: spacing.sm,
  },
  goalInfo: {
    flex: 1,
  },
  goalTitle: {
    fontSize: fontSize.md,
    fontFamily: 'Parkinsans-SemiBold',
    marginBottom: spacing.xs,
  },
  goalCategory: {
    fontSize: fontSize.sm,
    fontFamily: 'Parkinsans-Regular',
  },
  currentIndicator: {
    marginLeft: spacing.sm,
  },
  completedIndicator: {
    marginLeft: spacing.sm,
  },
  goalProgress: {
    marginTop: spacing.sm,
  },
  progressBar: {
    height: 6,
    borderRadius: 3,
    marginBottom: spacing.xs,
    overflow: 'hidden',
  },
  progressFill: {
    height: '100%',
    borderRadius: 3,
  },
  progressText: {
    fontSize: fontSize.sm,
    fontFamily: 'Parkinsans-Regular',
    textAlign: 'right',
  },
  separator: {
    height: spacing.xs,
  },
  loadingContainer: {
    flex: 1,
    justifyContent: 'center',
    alignItems: 'center',
    paddingVertical: spacing.xl,
  },
  loadingText: {
    fontSize: fontSize.md,
    fontFamily: 'Parkinsans-Regular',
  },
  emptyState: {
    flex: 1,
    justifyContent: 'center',
    alignItems: 'center',
    paddingVertical: spacing.xl,
  },
  emptyStateTitle: {
    fontSize: fontSize.lg,
    fontFamily: 'Parkinsans-SemiBold',
    marginTop: spacing.md,
    marginBottom: spacing.xs,
  },
  emptyStateText: {
    fontSize: fontSize.md,
    fontFamily: 'Parkinsans-Regular',
    textAlign: 'center',
    paddingHorizontal: spacing.lg,
  },
});

FILE: components/ErrorBoundary.tsx
================================================
import React, { Component, ErrorInfo, ReactNode } from 'react';
import { View, Text, TouchableOpacity, StyleSheet } from 'react-native';
import { useTheme } from '../contexts/ThemeContext';

interface Props {
  children: ReactNode;
}

interface State {
  hasError: boolean;
  error?: Error;
}

export class ErrorBoundary extends Component<Props, State> {
  constructor(props: Props) {
    super(props);
    this.state = { hasError: false };
  }

  static getDerivedStateFromError(error: Error): State {
    return { hasError: true, error };
  }

  componentDidCatch(error: Error, errorInfo: ErrorInfo) {
    console.error('Ã°Å¸Å¡Â¨ ErrorBoundary caught an error:', error, errorInfo);
  }

  handleRetry = () => {
    this.setState({ hasError: false, error: undefined });
  };

  render() {
    if (this.state.hasError) {
      return (
        <ErrorFallback 
          error={this.state.error} 
          onRetry={this.handleRetry} 
        />
      );
    }

    return this.props.children;
  }
}

interface ErrorFallbackProps {
  error?: Error;
  onRetry: () => void;
}

const ErrorFallback: React.FC<ErrorFallbackProps> = ({ error, onRetry }) => {
  const { colors } = useTheme();

  return (
    <View style={[styles.container, { backgroundColor: colors.background }]}>
      <Text style={[styles.title, { color: colors.text }]}>
        Ã°Å¸Å¡Â¨ Something went wrong
      </Text>
      <Text style={[styles.message, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>
        The app encountered an unexpected error. This might be due to a network issue or temporary problem.
      </Text>
      {error && (
        <Text style={[styles.errorDetails, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>
          Error: {error.message}
        </Text>
      )}
      <TouchableOpacity 
        style={[styles.retryButton, { backgroundColor: colors.primary }]}
        onPress={onRetry}
      >
        <Text style={[styles.retryButtonText, { color: colors.onPrimary }]}>
          Try Again
        </Text>
      </TouchableOpacity>
    </View>
  );
};

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
  container: {
    flex: 1,
    justifyContent: 'center',
    alignItems: 'center',
    padding: 20,
  },
  title: {
    fontSize: 24,
    fontWeight: 'bold',
    marginBottom: 16,
    textAlign: 'center',
  },
  message: {
    fontSize: 16,
    textAlign: 'center',
    marginBottom: 24,
    lineHeight: 24,
  },
  errorDetails: {
    fontSize: 12,
    textAlign: 'center',
    marginBottom: 24,
    fontFamily: 'monospace',
  },
  retryButton: {
    paddingHorizontal: 24,
    paddingVertical: 12,
    borderRadius: 8,
    minWidth: 120,
  },
  retryButtonText: {
    fontSize: 16,
    fontWeight: '600',
    textAlign: 'center',
  },
});



================================================
FILE: components/FluentEmoji.tsx

import React from 'react';
import { Image, ImageStyle, Text, TextStyle } from 'react-native';

interface FluentEmojiProps {
  emoji: string;
  size?: number;
  style?: ImageStyle | TextStyle;
  useImage?: boolean; // Whether to use image assets or text
}

// Microsoft Fluent Emoji mapping to actual PNG assets
const fluentEmojiMap: Record<string, any> = {
  // Money & Finance

  'ðŸ·': require('../assets/emojis/pig-face.png'),

  'ðŸ¸': require('../assets/emojis/frog.png'),
  'ðŸ±': require('../assets/emojis/cat-face.png'),
  'ðŸ¶': require('../assets/emojis/dog-face.png'),
  'ðŸ°': require('../assets/emojis/rabbit-face.png'),
  'ðŸ»': require('../assets/emojis/bear.png'),
  'ðŸ¦Š': require('../assets/emojis/fox.png'),
  
  // Progress Bar Emojis
  'ðŸ˜ƒ': require('../assets/emojis/grinning-face-big-eyes.png'),
  'ðŸ˜„': require('../assets/emojis/grinning-face-smiling-eyes.png'),
  'ðŸ˜Š': require('../assets/emojis/smiling-face-smiling-eyes.png'),
  'ðŸ˜': require('../assets/emojis/neutral-face.png'),
  'ðŸ˜”': require('../assets/emojis/pensive-face.png'),
  
  // Default fallback
  'default': require('../assets/emojis/money-bag.png'),
};

// Unicode fallback for emojis without assets
const unicodeEmojiMap: Record<string, string> = {
  'ðŸ¦': 'ðŸ›ï¸', // Classical building (more modern bank look)
  'ðŸ“ˆ': 'ðŸ“ˆ', // Chart increasing
  'ðŸ“‰': 'ðŸ“‰', // Chart decreasing
  'ðŸ½ï¸': 'ðŸ½ï¸', // Fork and knife with plate
  'ðŸ‘¨â€âš•ï¸': 'ðŸ‘¨â€âš•ï¸', // Health worker
  'ðŸ”': 'ðŸ”', // Magnifying glass (not available as asset)
  'ðŸ§': 'ðŸ’³', // ATM sign -> use credit card instead (now has Fluent asset)
  'ðŸ’»': 'ðŸ“±', // Laptop -> use mobile phone instead
  'ðŸ›¡ï¸': 'âœ…', // Shield -> use green tick instead
  
  // Default fallback
  'default': 'ðŸ’°',
};

export const FluentEmoji: React.FC<FluentEmojiProps> = ({ 
  emoji, 
  size = 24, 
  style,
  useImage = true
}) => {
  // Make emojis 15% larger
  const adjustedSize = size * 1.7;
  
  // First check if we need to map this emoji to a different one
  const mappedEmoji = unicodeEmojiMap[emoji] || emoji;
  
  // Check if we have a PNG asset for this emoji (after mapping)
  const hasImageAsset = fluentEmojiMap[mappedEmoji];
  
  if (useImage && hasImageAsset) {
    // Use the actual Microsoft Fluent Emoji PNG asset
    return (
      <Image
        source={fluentEmojiMap[mappedEmoji]}
        style={[
          {
            width: adjustedSize,
            height: adjustedSize,
          },
          style as ImageStyle
        ]}
        resizeMode="contain"
      />
    );
  } else {
    // Fallback to Unicode emoji
    const unicodeEmoji = mappedEmoji;
    
    return (
      <Text
        style={[
          {
            fontSize: adjustedSize,
            lineHeight: adjustedSize,
          },
          style as TextStyle
        ]}
      >
        {unicodeEmoji}
      </Text>
    );
  }
};

// Helper function to get fluent emoji (returns image source if available, otherwise Unicode)
export const getFluentEmoji = (emoji: string): any => {
  return fluentEmojiMap[emoji] || unicodeEmojiMap[emoji] || unicodeEmojiMap['default'];
};

// Helper function to check if emoji has image asset
export const hasFluentEmojiAsset = (emoji: string): boolean => {
  return !!fluentEmojiMap[emoji];
};

// Predefined emoji sets for different categories
export const fluentEmojis = {
  money: {

// Hook to replace all emojis in text with fluent versions
export const useFluentEmojis = (text: string): string => {
  return text.replace(/[\u{1F600}-\u{1F64F}]|[\u{1F300}-\u{1F5FF}]|[\u{1F680}-\u{1F6FF}]|[\u{1F1E0}-\u{1F1FF}]|[\u{2600}-\u{26FF}]|[\u{2700}-\u{27BF}]/gu, (match) => {
    return unicodeEmojiMap[match] || match;
  });
};



================================================
FILE: components/GoalCollaboration.tsx
================================================
import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react';
import {
  View,
  Text,
  StyleSheet,
  TouchableOpacity,
  ScrollView,
  Alert,
  Modal,
  Share,
  Linking,
} from 'react-native';
import { Ionicons } from '@expo/vector-icons';
import { useTheme } from '@/contexts/ThemeContext';
import { useAuth } from '@/contexts/AuthContext';
import { FluentEmoji } from '@/components/FluentEmoji';
import { normalizeFont, spacing, wp, hp } from '@/utils/responsive';
import { supabase } from '@/services/supabase';

interface GoalCollaborationProps {
  goalId: string;
  isOwner: boolean;
}

export const GoalCollaboration: React.FC<GoalCollaborationProps> = ({ goalId, isOwner }) => {
  const { colors } = useTheme();
  const { user } = useAuth();
  const [showShareModal, setShowShareModal] = useState(false);
  const [showMembersModal, setShowMembersModal] = useState(false);
  const [members, setMembers] = useState<any[]>([]);
  const [contributions, setContributions] = useState<any[]>([]);
  const [loading, setLoading] = useState(false);

  // Fetch goal members
  const fetchMembers = async () => {
    try {
      const { data, error } = await supabase
        .from('goal_members')
        .select(`
          *,
          users:user_id(id, email, name)
        `)
        .eq('goal_id', goalId);
      
      if (error) throw error;
      setMembers(data || []);
    } catch (error) {
      console.error('Error fetching members:', error);
    }
  };

  // Fetch goal contributions
  const fetchContributions = async () => {
    try {
      const { data, error } = await supabase
        .from('goal_contributions')
        .select(`
          *,
          users:user_id(id, email, name)
        `)
        .eq('goal_id', goalId)
        .order('contributed_at', { ascending: false });
      
      if (error) throw error;
      setContributions(data || []);
    } catch (error) {
      console.error('Error fetching contributions:', error);
    }
  };

  // Load data on component mount
  useEffect(() => {
    fetchMembers();
    fetchContributions();
  }, [goalId]);

  const handleShareGoal = async () => {
    try {
      const shareUrl = `noodl://goal/${goalId}`;
      const shareMessage = `Join me in saving for this goal! Click the link to contribute.`;
      
      const result = await Share.share({
        message: `${shareMessage}\n\n${shareUrl}`,
        url: shareUrl,
        title: 'Join My Savings Goal',
      });

      if (result.action === Share.sharedAction) {
        console.log('Goal shared successfully');
      }
    } catch (error) {
      console.error('Error sharing goal:', error);
      Alert.alert('Error', 'Failed to share goal. Please try again.');
    }
  };

  const handleCopyLink = async () => {
    try {
      const shareUrl = `noodl://goal/${goalId}`;
      // You can use a clipboard library here if needed
      Alert.alert('Link Copied', 'Goal link copied to clipboard!');
    } catch (error) {
      console.error('Error copying link:', error);
    }
  };

  const handleJoinGoal = async () => {
    try {
      // Check if user is already a member
      const { data: existingMember } = await supabase
        .from('goal_members')
        .select('id')
        .eq('goal_id', goalId)
        .eq('user_id', user?.id || '')
        .single();

      if (existingMember) {
        Alert.alert('Already a Member', 'You are already a member of this goal!');
        return;
      }

      // Add user as contributor
      const { error } = await supabase
        .from('goal_members')
        .insert({
          goal_id: goalId,
          user_id: user?.id || '',
          role: 'contributor',
          joined_at: new Date().toISOString(),
        });

      if (error) throw error;
      
      Alert.alert('Success', 'You have joined this goal! You can now contribute.');
      fetchMembers(); // Refresh the members list
    } catch (error) {
      console.error('Error joining goal:', error);
      Alert.alert('Error', 'Failed to join goal. Please try again.');
    }
  };

  const handleRemoveMember = async (memberId: string) => {
    Alert.alert(
      'Remove Member',
      'Are you sure you want to remove this member?',
      [
        { text: 'Cancel', style: 'cancel' },
        {
          text: 'Remove',
          style: 'destructive',
          onPress: async () => {
            try {
              const { error } = await supabase
                .from('goal_members')
                .delete()
                .eq('goal_id', goalId)
                .eq('user_id', memberId);

              if (error) throw error;
              
              Alert.alert('Success', 'Member removed successfully');
              fetchMembers(); // Refresh the members list
            } catch (error) {
              console.error('Error removing member:', error);
              Alert.alert('Error', 'Failed to remove member. Please try again.');
            }
          },
        },
      ]
    );
  };

  const getTotalContributions = () => {
    if (!contributions || contributions.length === 0) return 0;
    return contributions.reduce((total, contribution) => total + (contribution.amount || 0), 0);
  };

  const getMemberContributions = (memberId: string) => {
    if (!contributions || contributions.length === 0) return 0;
    return contributions
      .filter(contribution => contribution.user_id === memberId)
      .reduce((total, contribution) => total + (contribution.amount || 0), 0);
  };

  return (
    <View style={styles.container}>
      {/* Collaboration Header */}
      <View style={styles.header}>
        <Text style={[styles.title, { color: colors.text }]}>Collaboration</Text>
        <TouchableOpacity
          style={[styles.shareButton, { backgroundColor: colors.primary }]}
          onPress={() => setShowShareModal(true)}
        >
          <Ionicons name="share-outline" size={16} color="#FFFFFF" />
          <Text style={[styles.shareButtonText, { color: '#FFFFFF' }]}>Share</Text>
        </TouchableOpacity>
      </View>

      {/* Members Summary */}
      <View style={[styles.membersCard, { backgroundColor: colors.surface }]}>
        <View style={styles.membersHeader}>
          <FluentEmoji emoji="Ã°Å¸â€˜Â¥" size={20} />
          <Text style={[styles.membersTitle, { color: colors.text }]}>
            {members?.length || 1} Member{(members?.length || 1) !== 1 ? 's' : ''}
          </Text>
        </View>
        
        <View style={styles.membersActions}>
          <TouchableOpacity
            style={styles.viewMembersButton}
            onPress={() => setShowMembersModal(true)}
          >
            <Text style={[styles.viewMembersText, { color: colors.primary }]}>
              View Members
            </Text>
            <Ionicons name="chevron-forward" size={16} color={colors.primary} />
          </TouchableOpacity>
          
          {/* Show join button if user is not a member */}
          {!members.find(m => m.user_id === user?.id) && (
            <TouchableOpacity
              style={[styles.joinButton, { backgroundColor: colors.primary }]}
              onPress={handleJoinGoal}
            >
              <Ionicons name="person-add" size={16} color="#FFFFFF" />
              <Text style={[styles.joinButtonText, { color: '#FFFFFF' }]}>Join Goal</Text>
            </TouchableOpacity>
          )}
        </View>
      </View>

      {/* Contributions Summary */}
      <View style={[styles.contributionsCard, { backgroundColor: colors.surface }]}>
        <View style={styles.contributionsHeader}>
          <FluentEmoji emoji="Ã°Å¸â€™Â°" size={20} />
          <Text style={[styles.contributionsTitle, { color: colors.text }]}>
            Total Contributions
          </Text>
        </View>
        
        <Text style={[styles.contributionsAmount, { color: colors.primary }]}>
          ${getTotalContributions().toFixed(2)}
        </Text>
        
        <Text style={[styles.contributionsSubtext, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>
          From {contributions?.length || 0} contribution{(contributions?.length || 0) !== 1 ? 's' : ''}
        </Text>
      </View>

      {/* Share Modal */}
      <Modal
        visible={showShareModal}
        transparent
        animationType="slide"
        onRequestClose={() => setShowShareModal(false)}
      >
        <View style={styles.modalOverlay}>
          <View style={[styles.modalContent, { backgroundColor: colors.surface }]}>
            <View style={styles.modalHeader}>
              <Text style={[styles.modalTitle, { color: colors.text }]}>Share Goal</Text>
              <TouchableOpacity onPress={() => setShowShareModal(false)}>
                <Ionicons name="close" size={24} color={colors.text} />
              </TouchableOpacity>
            </View>
            
            <Text style={[styles.modalSubtitle, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>
              Share this goal with friends so they can contribute
            </Text>
            
            <View style={styles.shareOptions}>
              <TouchableOpacity
                style={[styles.shareOption, { backgroundColor: colors.primary }]}
                onPress={handleShareGoal}
              >
                <Ionicons name="share-social" size={24} color="#FFFFFF" />
                <Text style={[styles.shareOptionText, { color: '#FFFFFF' }]}>Share via App</Text>
              </TouchableOpacity>
              
              <TouchableOpacity
                style={[styles.shareOption, { backgroundColor: colors.background, borderColor: colors.border, borderWidth: 1 }]}
                onPress={handleCopyLink}
              >
                <Ionicons name="copy-outline" size={24} color={colors.primary} />
                <Text style={[styles.shareOptionText, { color: colors.primary }]}>Copy Link</Text>
              </TouchableOpacity>
            </View>
            
            <View style={styles.shareInfo}>
              <Text style={[styles.shareInfoText, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>
                When someone opens the shared link, they can join this goal and start contributing!
              </Text>
            </View>
          </View>
        </View>
      </Modal>

      {/* Members Modal */}
      <Modal
        visible={showMembersModal}
        transparent
        animationType="slide"
        onRequestClose={() => setShowMembersModal(false)}
      >
        <View style={styles.modalOverlay}>
          <View style={[styles.modalContent, { backgroundColor: colors.surface }]}>
            <View style={styles.modalHeader}>
              <Text style={[styles.modalTitle, { color: colors.text }]}>Goal Members</Text>
              <TouchableOpacity onPress={() => setShowMembersModal(false)}>
                <Ionicons name="close" size={24} color={colors.text} />
              </TouchableOpacity>
            </View>
            
            <ScrollView style={styles.membersList}>
                             {members.map((member) => (
                 <View key={member.id} style={styles.memberItem}>
                   <View style={styles.memberInfo}>
                     <View style={[styles.memberAvatar, { backgroundColor: colors.primary + '20' }]}>
                       <Text style={[styles.memberInitial, { color: colors.primary }]}>
                         {member.users?.name?.charAt(0) || member.users?.email?.charAt(0) || '?'}
                       </Text>
                     </View>
                     <View style={styles.memberDetails}>
                       <Text style={[styles.memberName, { color: colors.text }]}>
                         {member.users?.name || member.users?.email || 'Unknown User'}
                       </Text>
                       <Text style={[styles.memberRole, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>
                         {member.role.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + member.role.slice(1)}
                       </Text>
                       <Text style={[styles.memberContribution, { color: colors.primary }]}>
                         Contributed: ${getMemberContributions(member.user_id).toFixed(2)}
                       </Text>
                     </View>
                   </View>
                   
                   {isOwner && member.role !== 'owner' && (
                                           <TouchableOpacity
                        style={[styles.removeButton, { backgroundColor: '#FF6B6B' }]}
                        onPress={() => handleRemoveMember(member.user_id)}
                      >
                        <Ionicons name="person-remove" size={16} color="#FFFFFF" />
                      </TouchableOpacity>
                   )}
                 </View>
               ))}
            </ScrollView>
          </View>
        </View>
      </Modal>
    </View>
  );
};

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
  container: {
    marginBottom: spacing.lg,
  },
  header: {
    flexDirection: 'row',
    justifyContent: 'space-between',
    alignItems: 'center',
    marginBottom: spacing.md,
  },
  title: {
    fontSize: normalizeFont(18),
    fontFamily: 'Parkinsans-Bold',
  },
  shareButton: {
    flexDirection: 'row',
    alignItems: 'center',
    paddingHorizontal: spacing.md,
    paddingVertical: spacing.sm,
    borderRadius: 20,
    gap: spacing.xs,
  },
  shareButtonText: {
    fontSize: normalizeFont(14),
    fontFamily: 'Parkinsans-SemiBold',
  },
  membersCard: {
    borderRadius: 16,
    padding: spacing.md,
    marginBottom: spacing.md,
    shadowColor: '#000000',
    shadowOffset: { width: 0, height: 2 },
    shadowOpacity: 0.1,
    shadowRadius: 8,
    elevation: 4,
  },
  membersHeader: {
    flexDirection: 'row',
    alignItems: 'center',
    marginBottom: spacing.sm,
    gap: spacing.sm,
  },

FILE: components/GoalShareBottomSheet.tsx
================================================
import React, { useMemo, useRef, useState } from 'react';
import {
  View,
  Text,
  StyleSheet,
  TouchableOpacity,
  Share,
  Alert,
} from 'react-native';
import { Ionicons } from '@expo/vector-icons';
import { useTheme } from '@/contexts/ThemeContext';
import { FluentEmoji } from '@/components/FluentEmoji';
import { normalizeFont, spacing } from '@/utils/responsive';
import BottomSheet, { BottomSheetView, BottomSheetScrollView, BottomSheetBackdrop } from '@gorhom/bottom-sheet';
import * as Haptics from 'expo-haptics';
import * as Clipboard from 'expo-clipboard';

interface Goal {
  id: string;
  title: string;
  color?: string;
}

interface GoalShareBottomSheetProps {
  isVisible: boolean;
  goal: Goal | null;
  onClose: () => void;
}

export const GoalShareBottomSheet: React.FC<GoalShareBottomSheetProps> = ({
  isVisible,
  goal,
  onClose,
}) => {
  const { colors } = useTheme();
  const [copied, setCopied] = useState(false);

  // Bottom sheet ref and snap points
  const bottomSheetRef = useRef<BottomSheet>(null);
  const snapPoints = useMemo(() => ['90%'], []);

  // Load data when bottom sheet becomes visible
  React.useEffect(() => {
    if (isVisible && goal) {
      bottomSheetRef.current?.snapToIndex(0);
    } else {
      bottomSheetRef.current?.close();
    }
  }, [isVisible, goal]);

  // Don't render if no goal is selected
  if (!goal) return null;

  const handleShareGoal = async () => {
    try {
      const shareUrl = `noodl://goal/${goal.id}`;
      const shareMessage = `Join me in saving for "${goal.title}"! Click the link to contribute.`;
      
      const result = await Share.share({
        message: `${shareMessage}\n\n${shareUrl}`,
        url: shareUrl,
        title: 'Join My Savings Goal',
      });

      if (result.action === Share.sharedAction) {
        console.log('Goal shared successfully');
      }
    } catch (error) {
      console.error('Error sharing goal:', error);
      Alert.alert('Error', 'Failed to share goal. Please try again.');
    }
  };

  const handleCopyUuid = async () => {
    try {
      // Copy the goal UUID to clipboard
      await Clipboard.setStringAsync(goal.id);
      setCopied(true);
      setTimeout(() => setCopied(false), 2000);
      
      // Provide haptic feedback
      Haptics.impactAsync(Haptics.ImpactFeedbackStyle.Light);
      
      // Show success message
      Alert.alert('Success', `Goal UUID "${goal.id}" copied to clipboard!`);
    } catch (error) {
      console.error('Error copying UUID:', error);
      Alert.alert('Error', 'Failed to copy UUID to clipboard. Please try again.');
    }
  };

  const handleClose = () => {
    Haptics.impactAsync(Haptics.ImpactFeedbackStyle.Light);
    setCopied(false);
    onClose();
  };

  return (
    <BottomSheet
      ref={bottomSheetRef}
      index={isVisible ? 0 : -1}
      snapPoints={snapPoints}
      enablePanDownToClose
      onClose={handleClose}
      backgroundStyle={[styles.bottomSheetBackground, { backgroundColor: colors.background }]}
      handleIndicatorStyle={[styles.handleIndicator, { backgroundColor: colors.border }]}
      backdropComponent={(props) => (
        <BottomSheetBackdrop
          {...props}
          disappearsOnIndex={-1}
          appearsOnIndex={0}
          pressBehavior="close"
          opacity={0.8}
        />
      )}
    >
      <BottomSheetView style={styles.container}>
        {/* Header */}
        <View style={styles.header}>
          <Text style={[styles.headerTitle, { color: colors.text }]}>Share Goal</Text>
          <TouchableOpacity onPress={handleClose} style={styles.closeButton}>
            <Ionicons name="close" size={24} color={colors.text} />
          </TouchableOpacity>
        </View>

        <BottomSheetScrollView style={styles.content} showsVerticalScrollIndicator={false}>
          {/* Goal Info */}
          <View style={styles.goalInfo}>
            <View style={[styles.goalColor, { backgroundColor: goal.color || '#A2E57B' }]}>
              <FluentEmoji emoji="Ã°Å¸Å½Â¯" size={24} />
            </View>
            <Text style={[styles.headerTitle, { color: colors.text }]}>{goal.title}</Text>
          </View>
          
          <Text style={[styles.subtitle, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>
            Share this goal with friends so they can contribute
          </Text>
          
          {/* Share Options */}
          <View style={styles.shareOptions}>
            <TouchableOpacity
              style={[styles.shareOption, { backgroundColor: colors.primary }]}
              onPress={handleShareGoal}
            >
              <Ionicons name="share-social" size={24} color="#FFFFFF" />
              <Text style={[styles.shareOptionText, { color: '#FFFFFF' }]}>Share via App</Text>
            </TouchableOpacity>
            
            <TouchableOpacity
              style={[styles.shareOption, { backgroundColor: colors.background, borderColor: colors.border, borderWidth: 1 }]}
              onPress={handleCopyUuid}
            >
              <Ionicons name="copy-outline" size={24} color={colors.primary} />
              <Text style={[styles.shareOptionText, { color: colors.primary }]}>
                {copied ? 'Copied!' : 'Copy UUID'}
              </Text>
            </TouchableOpacity>
          </View>
          
          {/* UUID Section */}
          <View style={styles.uuidSection}>
            <Text style={[styles.uuidLabel, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>Goal UUID:</Text>
            <View style={[styles.uuidContainer, { backgroundColor: colors.surface }]}>
              <Text style={[styles.uuidText, { color: colors.text }]}>{goal.id}</Text>
            </View>
            <Text style={[styles.uuidInfo, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>
              Share this UUID with friends so they can join your goal
            </Text>
          </View>
          
          {/* Info */}
          <View style={[styles.infoContainer, { backgroundColor: colors.surface }]}>
            <Text style={[styles.infoText, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>
              When someone opens the shared link or enters the UUID, they can join this goal and start contributing!
            </Text>
          </View>
        </BottomSheetScrollView>
      </BottomSheetView>
    </BottomSheet>
  );
};

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
  bottomSheetBackground: {
    borderTopLeftRadius: 20,
    borderTopRightRadius: 20,
  },
  handleIndicator: {
    width: 40,
    height: 4,
    borderRadius: 2,
  },
  container: {
    flex: 1,
    paddingHorizontal: spacing.lg,
  },
  header: {
    flexDirection: 'row',
    justifyContent: 'space-between',
    alignItems: 'center',
    marginBottom: spacing.lg,
    paddingTop: spacing.md,
  },
  headerTitle: {
    fontSize: normalizeFont(20),
    fontFamily: 'Parkinsans-Bold',
  },
  closeButton: {
    width: 40,
    height: 40,
    borderRadius: 20,
    justifyContent: 'center',
    alignItems: 'center',
    backgroundColor: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.1)',
  },
  content: {
    flex: 1,
  },
  goalInfo: {
    flexDirection: 'row',
    alignItems: 'center',
    marginBottom: spacing.md,
    gap: spacing.md,
  },
  goalColor: {
    width: 40,
    height: 40,
    borderRadius: 20,
    justifyContent: 'center',
    alignItems: 'center',
  },
  subtitle: {
    fontSize: normalizeFont(16),
    fontFamily: 'Parkinsans-Regular',
    marginBottom: spacing.lg,
    textAlign: 'center',
  },
  shareOptions: {
    gap: spacing.md,
    marginBottom: spacing.lg,
  },
  shareOption: {
    flexDirection: 'row',
    alignItems: 'center',
    justifyContent: 'center',
    paddingVertical: spacing.md,

    borderRadius: 12,
    gap: spacing.sm,
  },
  shareOptionText: {
    fontSize: normalizeFont(16),
    fontFamily: 'Parkinsans-SemiBold',
  },
  uuidSection: {
    marginBottom: spacing.lg,
  },
  uuidLabel: {
    fontSize: normalizeFont(14),
    fontFamily: 'Parkinsans-SemiBold',
    marginBottom: spacing.sm,
  },
  uuidContainer: {
    padding: spacing.md,
    borderRadius: 12,
    marginBottom: spacing.sm,
  },
  uuidText: {
    fontSize: normalizeFont(14),
    fontFamily: 'monospace',
    textAlign: 'center',
  },
