FILE: components/JoinGoalBottomSheet.tsx
================================================
import React, { useMemo, useRef, useState } from 'react';
import {
  View,
  Text,
  StyleSheet,
  TouchableOpacity,
  TextInput,
  Alert,
} from 'react-native';
import { Ionicons } from '@expo/vector-icons';
import { useTheme } from '@/contexts/ThemeContext';
import { useAuth } from '@/contexts/AuthContext';
import { FluentEmoji } from '@/components/FluentEmoji';
import { normalizeFont, spacing } from '@/utils/responsive';
import { supabase } from '@/services/supabase';
import BottomSheet, { BottomSheetView, BottomSheetScrollView, BottomSheetBackdrop } from '@gorhom/bottom-sheet';
import * as Haptics from 'expo-haptics';

interface JoinGoalBottomSheetProps {
  isVisible: boolean;
  onClose: () => void;
  onGoalJoined: () => void;
}

export const JoinGoalBottomSheet: React.FC<JoinGoalBottomSheetProps> = ({
  isVisible,
  onClose,
  onGoalJoined,
}) => {
  const { colors } = useTheme();
  const { user } = useAuth();
  const [goalUuid, setGoalUuid] = useState('');
  const [loading, setLoading] = useState(false);

  // Bottom sheet ref and snap points
  const bottomSheetRef = useRef<BottomSheet>(null);
  const snapPoints = useMemo(() => ['90%'], []);

  // Load data when bottom sheet becomes visible
  React.useEffect(() => {
    if (isVisible) {
      bottomSheetRef.current?.snapToIndex(0);
    } else {
      bottomSheetRef.current?.close();
    }
  }, [isVisible]);

  const handleJoinGoal = async () => {
    if (!goalUuid.trim()) {
      Alert.alert('Error', 'Please enter a goal UUID');
      return;
    }

    try {
      setLoading(true);
      Haptics.impactAsync(Haptics.ImpactFeedbackStyle.Medium);

      // First, check if the goal exists
      const { data: goal, error: goalError } = await supabase
        .from('goals')
        .select('id, title, user_id')
        .eq('id', goalUuid.trim())
        .single();

      if (goalError || !goal) {
        Alert.alert('Error', 'Goal not found. Please check the UUID and try again.');
        return;
      }

      // Check if user is already a member
      const { data: existingMember } = await supabase
        .from('goal_members')
        .select('id')
        .eq('goal_id', goal.id)
        .eq('user_id', user?.id || '')
        .single();

      if (existingMember) {
        Alert.alert('Already a Member', 'You are already a member of this goal!');
        return;
      }

      // Add user as contributor
      const { error } = await supabase
        .from('goal_members')
        .insert({
          goal_id: goal.id,
          user_id: user?.id || '',
          role: 'contributor',
          joined_at: new Date().toISOString(),
        });

      if (error) throw error;
      
      Alert.alert('Success', `You have joined the goal "${goal.title}"! You can now contribute.`);
      setGoalUuid('');
      onGoalJoined();
      onClose();
    } catch (error) {
      console.error('Error joining goal:', error);
      Alert.alert('Error', 'Failed to join goal. Please try again.');
    } finally {
      setLoading(false);
    }
  };

  const handleClose = () => {
    Haptics.impactAsync(Haptics.ImpactFeedbackStyle.Light);
    setGoalUuid('');
    onClose();
  };

  return (
    <BottomSheet
      ref={bottomSheetRef}
      index={isVisible ? 0 : -1}
      snapPoints={snapPoints}
      enablePanDownToClose
      onClose={handleClose}
      backgroundStyle={[styles.bottomSheetBackground, { backgroundColor: colors.background }]}
      handleIndicatorStyle={[styles.handleIndicator, { backgroundColor: colors.border }]}
      backdropComponent={(props) => (
        <BottomSheetBackdrop
          {...props}
          disappearsOnIndex={-1}
          appearsOnIndex={0}
          pressBehavior="close"
          opacity={0.8}
        />
      )}
    >
      <BottomSheetView style={styles.container}>
        {/* Header */}
        <View style={styles.header}>
          <Text style={[styles.headerTitle, { color: colors.text }]}>Join Goal</Text>
          <TouchableOpacity onPress={handleClose} style={styles.closeButton}>
            <Ionicons name="close" size={24} color={colors.text} />
          </TouchableOpacity>
        </View>

        <BottomSheetScrollView style={styles.content} showsVerticalScrollIndicator={false}>
          {/* Emoji */}
          <View style={styles.emojiContainer}>
            <FluentEmoji emoji="Ã°Å¸â€˜Â¥" size={48} />
          </View>
          
          <Text style={[styles.subtitle, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>
            Enter the goal UUID to join and start contributing
          </Text>
          
          {/* UUID Input */}
          <View style={styles.inputGroup}>
            <Text style={[styles.label, { color: colors.text }]}>Goal UUID</Text>
            <TextInput
              style={[styles.input, { 
                backgroundColor: colors.surface,
                borderColor: colors.border,
                color: colors.text
              }]}
              placeholder="Enter goal UUID"
              placeholderTextColor={colors.textSecondary}
              value={goalUuid}
              onChangeText={setGoalUuid}
              autoCapitalize="none"
              autoCorrect={false}
            />
          </View>
          
          {/* Action Buttons */}
          <View style={styles.buttonGroup}>
            <TouchableOpacity
              style={[styles.cancelButton, { backgroundColor: colors.border }]}
              onPress={handleClose}
            >
              <Text style={[styles.cancelButtonText, { color: colors.text }]}>Cancel</Text>
            </TouchableOpacity>
            <TouchableOpacity
              style={[styles.joinButton, { backgroundColor: colors.primary }]}
              onPress={handleJoinGoal}
              disabled={loading}
            >
              <Text style={[styles.joinButtonText, { color: '#FFFFFF' }]}>
                {loading ? 'Joining...' : 'Join Goal'}
              </Text>
            </TouchableOpacity>
          </View>
          
          {/* Info */}
          <View style={[styles.infoContainer, { backgroundColor: colors.surface }]}>
            <Text style={[styles.infoText, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>
              You can find the goal UUID in the goal details or ask the goal owner to share it with you.
            </Text>
          </View>
        </BottomSheetScrollView>
      </BottomSheetView>
    </BottomSheet>
  );
};

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
  bottomSheetBackground: {
    borderTopLeftRadius: 20,
    borderTopRightRadius: 20,
  },
  handleIndicator: {
    width: 40,
    height: 4,
    borderRadius: 2,
  },
  container: {
    flex: 1,
    paddingHorizontal: spacing.lg,
  },
  header: {
    flexDirection: 'row',
    justifyContent: 'space-between',
    alignItems: 'center',
    marginBottom: spacing.lg,
    paddingTop: spacing.md,
  },
  headerTitle: {
    fontSize: normalizeFont(20),
    fontFamily: 'Parkinsans-Bold',
  },
  closeButton: {
    width: 40,
    height: 40,
    borderRadius: 20,
    justifyContent: 'center',
    alignItems: 'center',
    backgroundColor: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.1)',
  },
  content: {
    flex: 1,
  },
  emojiContainer: {
    alignItems: 'center',
    marginBottom: spacing.md,
  },
  subtitle: {
    fontSize: normalizeFont(16),
    fontFamily: 'Parkinsans-Regular',
    marginBottom: spacing.lg,
    textAlign: 'center',
  },
  inputGroup: {
    marginBottom: spacing.lg,
  },
  label: {
    fontSize: normalizeFont(16),
    fontFamily: 'Parkinsans-SemiBold',
    marginBottom: spacing.sm,
  },
  input: {
    borderWidth: 1,
    borderRadius: 12,
    padding: spacing.md,
    fontSize: normalizeFont(16),

  },
  buttonGroup: {
    flexDirection: 'row',

    marginBottom: spacing.lg,
  },

    flex: 1,

    borderRadius: 12,

  },
  cancelButtonText: {

  },
  joinButton: {
    flex: 1,
    paddingVertical: spacing.md,
    borderRadius: 12,

  },

  },

    marginBottom: spacing.lg,

FILE: components/LevelDisplay.tsx
================================================
import React from 'react';
import { View, Text, StyleSheet } from 'react-native';
import { LevelService, LevelInfo } from '../services/levelService';

interface LevelDisplayProps {
  xp: number;
  showProgress?: boolean;
  size?: 'small' | 'medium' | 'large';
}

export const LevelDisplay: React.FC<LevelDisplayProps> = ({ 
  xp, 
  showProgress = true, 
  size = 'medium' 
}) => {
  const levelInfo = LevelService.calculateLevel(xp);
  const badge = LevelService.getLevelBadge(levelInfo.rank);
  const color = LevelService.getLevelColor(levelInfo.rank);
  const nextRankInfo = LevelService.getNextRankInfo(xp);

  const sizeStyles = {
    small: { fontSize: 12, badgeSize: 16 },
    medium: { fontSize: 14, badgeSize: 20 },
    large: { fontSize: 18, badgeSize: 24 }
  };

  const currentSize = sizeStyles[size];

  return (
    <View style={styles.container}>
      <View style={styles.rankContainer}>
        <Text style={[styles.badge, { fontSize: currentSize.badgeSize }]}>
          {badge}
        </Text>
        <Text style={[styles.rank, { fontSize: currentSize.fontSize, color }]}>
          {levelInfo.rank}
        </Text>
      </View>
      
      {showProgress && nextRankInfo && (
        <View style={styles.progressContainer}>
          <View style={styles.progressBar}>
            <View 
              style={[
                styles.progressFill, 
                { 
                  width: `${levelInfo.progressToNextLevel}%`,
                  backgroundColor: color 
                }
              ]} 
            />
          </View>
          <Text style={[styles.progressText, { fontSize: currentSize.fontSize - 2 }]}>
            {levelInfo.progressToNextLevel}% to {nextRankInfo.rank}
          </Text>
        </View>
      )}
      
      {showProgress && !nextRankInfo && (
        <Text style={[styles.maxLevelText, { fontSize: currentSize.fontSize - 2 }]}>
          Ã°Å¸Å½â€° Max level reached!
        </Text>
      )}
    </View>
  );
};

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
  container: {
    alignItems: 'center',
  },
  rankContainer: {
    flexDirection: 'row',
    alignItems: 'center',
    gap: 8,
  },
  badge: {
    fontSize: 20,
  },
  rank: {
    fontWeight: 'bold',
    textAlign: 'center',
  },
  progressContainer: {
    marginTop: 8,
    alignItems: 'center',
    width: '100%',
  },
  progressBar: {
    width: '100%',
    height: 6,
    backgroundColor: '#E5E7EB',
    borderRadius: 3,
    overflow: 'hidden',
  },
  progressFill: {
    height: '100%',
    borderRadius: 3,
  },
  progressText: {
    marginTop: 4,
    color: '#6B7280',
    textAlign: 'center',
  },
  maxLevelText: {
    marginTop: 8,
    color: '#10B981',
    fontWeight: 'bold',
    textAlign: 'center',
  },
});

FILE: components/LevelUpCelebration.tsx
================================================
import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react';
import { View, Text, StyleSheet, Animated, Dimensions } from 'react-native';
import LottieView from 'lottie-react-native';
import { LevelService } from '../services/levelService';

interface LevelUpCelebrationProps {
  oldXP: number;
  newXP: number;
  onComplete?: () => void;
}

const { width, height } = Dimensions.get('window');

export const LevelUpCelebration: React.FC<LevelUpCelebrationProps> = ({
  oldXP,
  newXP,
  onComplete
}) => {
  const [show, setShow] = useState(false);
  const [oldRank, setOldRank] = useState('');
  const [newRank, setNewRank] = useState('');
  
  const scaleAnim = new Animated.Value(0);
  const opacityAnim = new Animated.Value(0);

  useEffect(() => {
    if (LevelService.hasLeveledUp(oldXP, newXP)) {
      setOldRank(LevelService.getRankForXP(oldXP));
      setNewRank(LevelService.getRankForXP(newXP));
      setShow(true);
      
      // Animate in
      Animated.parallel([
        Animated.spring(scaleAnim, {
          toValue: 1,
          useNativeDriver: true,
          tension: 100,
          friction: 8,
        }),
        Animated.timing(opacityAnim, {
          toValue: 1,
          duration: 300,
          useNativeDriver: true,
        }),
      ]).start();
      
      // Auto-hide after 4 seconds
      setTimeout(() => {
        hideCelebration();
      }, 4000);
    }
  }, [oldXP, newXP]);

  const hideCelebration = () => {
    Animated.parallel([
      Animated.spring(scaleAnim, {
        toValue: 0,
        useNativeDriver: true,
        tension: 100,
        friction: 8,
      }),
      Animated.timing(opacityAnim, {
        toValue: 0,
        duration: 300,
        useNativeDriver: true,
      }),
    ]).start(() => {
      setShow(false);
      onComplete?.();
    });
  };

  if (!show) return null;

  return (
    <View style={styles.overlay}>
      <Animated.View 
        style={[
          styles.container,
          {
            opacity: opacityAnim,
            transform: [{ scale: scaleAnim }],
          }
        ]}
      >
        {/* Confetti Animation */}
        <View style={styles.confettiContainer}>
          <LottieView
            source={require('../assets/animations/confetti.json')}
            autoPlay
            loop={false}
            style={styles.confetti}
          />
        </View>
        
        {/* Level Up Content */}
        <View style={styles.content}>
          <Text style={styles.title}>Ã°Å¸Å½â€° LEVEL UP! Ã°Å¸Å½â€°</Text>
          
          <View style={styles.rankChange}>
            <View style={styles.oldRank}>
              <Text style={styles.rankLabel}>From</Text>
              <Text style={styles.oldRankText}>{oldRank}</Text>
            </View>
            
            <Text style={styles.arrow}>Ã¢â€ â€™</Text>
            
            <View style={styles.newRank}>
              <Text style={styles.rankLabel}>To</Text>
              <Text style={[styles.newRankText, { color: LevelService.getLevelColor(newRank) }]}>
                {newRank}
              </Text>
            </View>
          </View>
          
          <Text style={styles.badge}>
            {LevelService.getLevelBadge(newRank)}
          </Text>
          
          <Text style={styles.congrats}>
            Congratulations! You've reached a new level of financial wisdom!
          </Text>
        </View>
      </Animated.View>
    </View>
  );
};

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
  overlay: {
    position: 'absolute',
    top: 0,
    left: 0,
    right: 0,
    bottom: 0,
    backgroundColor: 'rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8)',
    justifyContent: 'center',
    alignItems: 'center',
    zIndex: 1000,
  },
  container: {
    backgroundColor: '#FFFFFF',
    borderRadius: 20,
    padding: 30,
    alignItems: 'center',
    maxWidth: width * 0.9,
    shadowColor: '#000',
    shadowOffset: { width: 0, height: 10 },
    shadowOpacity: 0.3,
    shadowRadius: 20,
    elevation: 10,
  },
  confettiContainer: {
    position: 'absolute',
    top: -50,
    left: -50,
    right: -50,
    bottom: -50,
  },
  confetti: {
    width: '100%',
    height: '100%',
  },
  content: {
    alignItems: 'center',
    zIndex: 1,
  },
  title: {
    fontSize: 24,
    fontWeight: 'bold',
    color: '#1F2937',
    marginBottom: 20,
    textAlign: 'center',
  },
  rankChange: {
    flexDirection: 'row',

    marginBottom: 20,
  },
  oldRank: {
    alignItems: 'center',
    marginRight: 20,
  },

FILE: components/LumaSpin.tsx
================================================
import React, { useEffect, useRef } from 'react';
import { View, Animated, StyleSheet } from 'react-native';
import { useTheme } from '../contexts/ThemeContext';

interface LumaSpinProps {
  size?: number;
  color?: string;
  variant?: 'default' | 'small' | 'large';
  speed?: 'slow' | 'normal' | 'fast';
}

export const LumaSpin: React.FC<LumaSpinProps> = ({ 
  size,
  color,
  variant = 'default',
  speed = 'normal'
}) => {
  const { colors } = useTheme();
  const dot1Opacity = useRef(new Animated.Value(0)).current;
  const dot2Opacity = useRef(new Animated.Value(0)).current;
  const dot3Opacity = useRef(new Animated.Value(0)).current;

  // Determine size based on variant if not explicitly provided
  const finalSize = size || (variant === 'small' ? 40 : variant === 'large' ? 80 : 65);
  
  // Determine color based on theme and props
  const dotColor = color || colors.primary;
  
  // Determine speed based on prop
  const duration = speed === 'slow' ? 800 : speed === 'fast' ? 400 : 600;

  useEffect(() => {
    const animateDots = () => {
      // Reset all dots
      dot1Opacity.setValue(0);
      dot2Opacity.setValue(0);
      dot3Opacity.setValue(0);

      // Animate dot 1
      Animated.sequence([
        Animated.timing(dot1Opacity, {
          toValue: 1,
          duration: duration / 2,
          useNativeDriver: true,
        }),
        Animated.timing(dot1Opacity, {
          toValue: 0,
          duration: duration / 2,
          useNativeDriver: true,
        }),
      ]).start();

      // Animate dot 2 with delay
      Animated.sequence([
        Animated.delay(duration / 3),
        Animated.timing(dot2Opacity, {
          toValue: 1,
          duration: duration / 2,
          useNativeDriver: true,
        }),
        Animated.timing(dot2Opacity, {
          toValue: 0,
          duration: duration / 2,
          useNativeDriver: true,
        }),
      ]).start();

      // Animate dot 3 with delay
      Animated.sequence([
        Animated.delay((duration / 3) * 2),
        Animated.timing(dot3Opacity, {
          toValue: 1,
          duration: duration / 2,
          useNativeDriver: true,
        }),
        Animated.timing(dot3Opacity, {
          toValue: 0,
          duration: duration / 2,
          useNativeDriver: true,
        }),
      ]).start();
    };

    const interval = setInterval(animateDots, duration * 2);
    animateDots(); // Start immediately

    return () => {
      clearInterval(interval);
    };
  }, [dot1Opacity, dot2Opacity, dot3Opacity, duration]);

  const dotSize = finalSize * 0.15; // Proportional dot size
  const spacing = finalSize * 0.1; // Space between dots

  return (
    <View style={[styles.container, { width: finalSize, height: finalSize }]}>
      <View style={styles.dotsContainer}>
        <Animated.View 
          style={[
            styles.dot,
            { 
              backgroundColor: dotColor,
              width: dotSize,
              height: dotSize,
              borderRadius: dotSize / 2,
              marginRight: spacing,
              opacity: dot1Opacity
            }
          ]} 
        />
        <Animated.View 
          style={[
            styles.dot,
            { 
              backgroundColor: dotColor,
              width: dotSize,
              height: dotSize,
              borderRadius: dotSize / 2,
              marginRight: spacing,
              opacity: dot2Opacity
            }
          ]} 
        />
        <Animated.View 
          style={[
            styles.dot,
            { 
              backgroundColor: dotColor,
              width: dotSize,
              height: dotSize,
              borderRadius: dotSize / 2,
              opacity: dot3Opacity
            }
          ]} 
        />
      </View>
    </View>
  );
};

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
  container: {
    justifyContent: 'center',
    alignItems: 'center',
  },
  dotsContainer: {
    flexDirection: 'row',
    alignItems: 'center',
    justifyContent: 'center',
  },
  dot: {
    // Styles applied inline for dynamic sizing
  },
});

FILE: components/SimpleNotificationSettings.tsx
================================================
import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react';
import { View, Text, StyleSheet, Switch, TouchableOpacity } from 'react-native';
import { useTheme } from '../contexts/ThemeContext';
import { useAuth } from '../contexts/AuthContext';
import { supabase } from '../services/supabase';
import { oneSignalService } from '../services/oneSignal';

export default function SimpleNotificationSettings() {
  const { colors } = useTheme();
  const { user } = useAuth();
  const [notificationsEnabled, setNotificationsEnabled] = useState(false);
  const [loading, setLoading] = useState(true);

  useEffect(() => {
    loadNotificationSettings();
  }, []);

  const loadNotificationSettings = async () => {
    try {
      if (!user?.id) return;

      const { data, error } = await supabase
        .from('users')
        .select('notification_preferences')
        .eq('id', user.id)
        .single();

      if (error) {
        console.error('Error loading notification settings:', error);
        return;
      }

      const preferences = data?.notification_preferences || {};
      setNotificationsEnabled(preferences.enabled !== false); // Default to true
    } catch (error) {
      console.error('Error loading notification settings:', error);
    } finally {
      setLoading(false);
    }
  };

  const toggleNotifications = async (value: boolean) => {
    try {
      if (!user?.id) return;

      setNotificationsEnabled(value);

      // Update database
      const { error } = await supabase
        .from('users')
        .update({
          notification_preferences: {
            enabled: value
          }
        })
        .eq('id', user.id);

      if (error) {
        console.error('Error updating notification settings:', error);
        // Revert the toggle if update failed
        setNotificationsEnabled(!value);
        return;
      }

      // Update OneSignal
      if (value) {
        await oneSignalService.enableNotifications();
      } else {
        await oneSignalService.disableNotifications();
      }

      console.log('Ã¢Å“â€¦ Notification settings updated:', value);
    } catch (error) {
      console.error('Error toggling notifications:', error);
      // Revert the toggle if update failed
      setNotificationsEnabled(!value);
    }
  };

  if (loading) {
    return (
      <View style={[styles.container, { backgroundColor: colors.background }]}>
        <Text style={[styles.loadingText, { color: colors.text }]}>Loading...</Text>
      </View>
    );
  }

  return (
    <View style={[styles.container, { backgroundColor: colors.background }]}>
      <View style={styles.header}>
        <Text style={[styles.title, { color: colors.text }]}>Notifications</Text>
        <Text style={[styles.subtitle, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>
          Receive push notifications for important updates
        </Text>
      </View>

      <View style={[styles.toggleContainer, { backgroundColor: colors.cardBackground }]}>
        <View style={styles.toggleLeft}>
          <Text style={[styles.toggleLabel, { color: colors.text }]}>
            Push Notifications
          </Text>
          <Text style={[styles.toggleDescription, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>
            {notificationsEnabled ? 'Notifications are enabled' : 'Notifications are disabled'}
          </Text>
        </View>
        
        <Switch
          value={notificationsEnabled}
          onValueChange={toggleNotifications}
          trackColor={{ false: colors.border, true: colors.primary }}
          thumbColor={notificationsEnabled ? colors.background : colors.textSecondary}
          ios_backgroundColor={colors.border}
        />
      </View>

      <View style={styles.infoContainer}>
        <Text style={[styles.infoText, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>
          You'll receive notifications for:
        </Text>
        <Text style={[styles.infoText, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>
          Ã¢â‚¬Â¢ Daily challenges
        </Text>
        <Text style={[styles.infoText, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>
          Ã¢â‚¬Â¢ Friend requests
        </Text>
        <Text style={[styles.infoText, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>
          Ã¢â‚¬Â¢ Level ups and achievements
        </Text>
      </View>
    </View>
  );
}

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
  container: {
    flex: 1,
    padding: 20,
  },
  header: {
    marginBottom: 30,
  },
  title: {
    fontSize: 28,
    fontFamily: 'Parkinsans-Bold',
    marginBottom: 8,
  },
  subtitle: {
    fontSize: 16,
    fontFamily: 'Parkinsans-Regular',
    lineHeight: 22,
  },
  toggleContainer: {
    flexDirection: 'row',
    alignItems: 'center',
    justifyContent: 'space-between',
    padding: 20,
    borderRadius: 16,
    marginBottom: 30,
    shadowColor: '#000',
    shadowOffset: {
      width: 0,
      height: 2,
    },
    shadowOpacity: 0.1,
    shadowRadius: 8,
    elevation: 3,
  },
  toggleLeft: {
    flex: 1,
    marginRight: 20,
  },
  toggleLabel: {
    fontSize: 18,
    fontFamily: 'Parkinsans-SemiBold',
    marginBottom: 4,
  },
  toggleDescription: {
    fontSize: 14,
    fontFamily: 'Parkinsans-Regular',
    lineHeight: 18,
  },
  infoContainer: {
    padding: 20,
    borderRadius: 16,
    backgroundColor: 'rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03)',
  },
  infoText: {
    fontSize: 14,
    fontFamily: 'Parkinsans-Regular',
    lineHeight: 20,
    marginBottom: 4,
  },
  loadingText: {
    fontSize: 16,
    fontFamily: 'Parkinsans-Regular',
    textAlign: 'center',
    marginTop: 50,
  },
});

FILE: components/SmartGoalsBottomSheet.tsx

import React, { useCallback, useMemo, useRef, useState } from 'react';
import {
  View,
  Text,
  StyleSheet,
  TouchableOpacity,
  Dimensions,
  Alert,
} from 'react-native';
import { Ionicons } from '@expo/vector-icons';
import { useTheme } from '@/contexts/ThemeContext';
import { SmartGoalsService, SmartGoal } from '@/services/smartGoalsService';
import { normalizeFont, spacing } from '@/utils/responsive';
import * as Haptics from 'expo-haptics';
import { LinearGradient } from 'expo-linear-gradient';
import BottomSheet, { BottomSheetView, BottomSheetScrollView } from '@gorhom/bottom-sheet';

const { width } = Dimensions.get('window');

interface SmartGoalsBottomSheetProps {
  isVisible: boolean;
  onClose: () => void;
  onGoalCreated: (goal: SmartGoal) => void;
}

export const SmartGoalsBottomSheet: React.FC<SmartGoalsBottomSheetProps> = ({
  isVisible,
  onClose,
  onGoalCreated,
}) => {
  const { colors } = useTheme();
  const [activeTab, setActiveTab] = useState<'insights' | 'goals' | 'create'>('insights');
  const [goals, setGoals] = useState<SmartGoal[]>([]);
  const [insights, setInsights] = useState<any[]>([]);
  const [financialHealth, setFinancialHealth] = useState<{ score: number; breakdown: any }>({ score: 0, breakdown: {} });
  const [loading, setLoading] = useState(false);

  // Bottom sheet ref and snap points
  const bottomSheetRef = useRef<BottomSheet>(null);
  const snapPoints = useMemo(() => ['25%', '50%', '90%'], []);

  // Load data when bottom sheet becomes visible
  React.useEffect(() => {
    if (isVisible) {
      loadSmartData();
      bottomSheetRef.current?.snapToIndex(1);
    }
  }, [isVisible]);

  const loadSmartData = async () => {
    try {
      setLoading(true);
      const [goalsData, insightsData, healthData] = await Promise.all([
        SmartGoalsService.getGoals(),
        SmartGoalsService.getAIInsights(),
        SmartGoalsService.getFinancialHealthScore()
      ]);
      setGoals(goalsData);
      setInsights(insightsData);
      setFinancialHealth(healthData);
    } catch (error) {
      console.error('Error loading smart data:', error);
    } finally {
      setLoading(false);
    }
  };

  const handleTabPress = (tab: 'insights' | 'goals' | 'create') => {
    Haptics.impactAsync(Haptics.ImpactFeedbackStyle.Light);
    setActiveTab(tab);
  };

  const handleClose = () => {
    Haptics.impactAsync(Haptics.ImpactFeedbackStyle.Light);
    onClose();
  };

  const getHealthScoreColor = (score: number) => {
    if (score >= 80) return '#4ECDC4';
    if (score >= 60) return '#F7DC6F';
    return '#FF6B6B';
  };

  const getPriorityIcon = (priority: number) => {
    switch (priority) {
      case 1: return 'Ã°Å¸â€Â¥';
      case 2: return 'Ã¢Å¡Â¡';
      case 3: return 'Ã°Å¸â€œÅ’';
      case 4: return 'Ã°Å¸â€™Â¡';
      case 5: return 'Ã¢Å“Â¨';
      default: return 'Ã°Å¸â€œÅ’';
    }
  };

  const renderInsightsTab = () => (
    <View style={styles.tabContent}>
      <Text style={[styles.tabTitle, { color: colors.text }]}>AI Insights</Text>
      
      {/* Financial Health Score */}
      <View style={[styles.healthCard, { backgroundColor: colors.surface }]}>
        <LinearGradient
          colors={[getHealthScoreColor(financialHealth.score), getHealthScoreColor(financialHealth.score + 20)]}
          style={styles.healthScoreCircle}
          start={{ x: 0, y: 0 }}
          end={{ x: 1, y: 1 }}
        >
          <Text style={styles.healthScoreNumber}>{Math.round(financialHealth.score)}</Text>
          <Text style={styles.healthScoreLabel}>/100</Text>
        </LinearGradient>
        
        <View style={styles.healthBreakdown}>
          <View style={styles.healthMetric}>
            <Text style={[styles.metricLabel, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>Emergency Fund</Text>
            <Text style={[styles.metricValue, { color: colors.text }]}>
              {financialHealth.breakdown.emergency_fund || 0} months
            </Text>
          </View>
          <View style={styles.healthMetric}>
            <Text style={[styles.metricLabel, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>Savings Rate</Text>
            <Text style={[styles.metricValue, { color: colors.text }]}>
              {(financialHealth.breakdown.savings_rate || 0).toFixed(1)}%
            </Text>
          </View>
        </View>
      </View>

      {/* AI Insights */}
      {insights.length > 0 ? (
        <View style={styles.insightsList}>
          {insights.slice(0, 3).map((insight, index) => (
            <TouchableOpacity
              key={insight.id || index}
              style={[styles.insightCard, { backgroundColor: colors.surface }]}
              onPress={() => {
                Haptics.impactAsync(Haptics.ImpactFeedbackStyle.Light);
                Alert.alert(insight.title, insight.actionable_advice || insight.description);
              }}
            >
              <View style={styles.insightHeader}>
                <Text style={styles.insightIcon}>Ã°Å¸â€™Â¡</Text>
                <View style={[styles.priorityBadge, { backgroundColor: colors.primary }]}>
                  <Text style={styles.priorityText}>P{insight.priority_level || 3}</Text>
                </View>
              </View>
              <Text style={[styles.insightTitle, { color: colors.text }]} numberOfLines={2}>
                {insight.title}
              </Text>
              <Text style={[styles.insightDescription, { color: colors.textSecondary }]} numberOfLines={2}>
                {insight.description}
              </Text>
            </TouchableOpacity>
          ))}
        </View>
      ) : (
        <View style={[styles.emptyState, { backgroundColor: colors.surface }]}>
          <Ionicons name="bulb" size={32} color={colors.primary} />
          <Text style={[styles.emptyText, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>
            No insights yet. Create some goals to get started!
          </Text>
        </View>
      )}
    </View>
  );

  const renderGoalsTab = () => (
    <View style={styles.tabContent}>
      <Text style={[styles.tabTitle, { color: colors.text }]}>Smart Goals</Text>
      
      {goals.length > 0 ? (
        <View style={styles.goalsList}>
          {goals.slice(0, 4).map((goal) => (
            <TouchableOpacity
              key={goal.id}
              style={[styles.goalCard, { backgroundColor: colors.surface }]}
              onPress={() => {
                Haptics.impactAsync(Haptics.ImpactFeedbackStyle.Light);
                // Navigate to goal details or show actions
              }}
            >
              <View style={styles.goalHeader}>
                <Text style={styles.priorityIcon}>{getPriorityIcon(goal.priority)}</Text>
                <View style={[styles.goalColor, { backgroundColor: goal.color }]} />
              </View>
              
              <Text style={[styles.goalTitle, { color: colors.text }]} numberOfLines={1}>
                {goal.title}
              </Text>
              
              <View style={styles.goalProgress}>
                <View style={[styles.progressBar, { backgroundColor: colors.border }]}>
                  <View 
                    style={[
                      styles.progressFill, 
                      { 
                        backgroundColor: goal.color,
                        width: `${Math.min(100, (goal.current_amount / goal.target_amount) * 100)}%`
                      }
                    ]} 
                  />
                </View>
                <Text style={[styles.progressText, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>
                  ${goal.current_amount.toLocaleString()} / ${goal.target_amount.toLocaleString()}
                </Text>
              </View>
            </TouchableOpacity>
          ))}
        </View>
      ) : (
                 <View style={[styles.emptyState, { backgroundColor: colors.surface }]}>
           <Ionicons name="flag" size={32} color={colors.primary} />
           <Text style={[styles.emptyText, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>
             No smart goals yet. Create your first one!
           </Text>
         </View>
      )}
    </View>
  );

  const renderCreateTab = () => (
    <View style={styles.tabContent}>
      <Text style={[styles.tabTitle, { color: colors.text }]}>Create Smart Goal</Text>
      
      <View style={[styles.createCard, { backgroundColor: colors.surface }]}>
        <Ionicons name="bulb" size={48} color={colors.primary} />
        <Text style={[styles.createTitle, { color: colors.text }]}>
          AI-Optimized Goals
        </Text>
        <Text style={[styles.createDescription, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>
          Create intelligent financial goals with personalized recommendations, risk assessment, and behavioral tracking.
        </Text>
        
                 <TouchableOpacity
           style={[styles.createButton, { backgroundColor: colors.primary }]}
           onPress={() => {
             Haptics.impactAsync(Haptics.ImpactFeedbackStyle.Medium);
             // Open the smart goal creator modal
             onGoalCreated({} as SmartGoal);
           }}
         >
          <Ionicons name="add" size={20} color="#FFFFFF" />
          <Text style={styles.createButtonText}>Create Smart Goal</Text>
        </TouchableOpacity>
      </View>

      <View style={[styles.featuresCard, { backgroundColor: colors.surface }]}>
        <Text style={[styles.featuresTitle, { color: colors.text }]}>Smart Features</Text>
        <View style={styles.featuresList}>
          <View style={styles.featureItem}>
            <Ionicons name="trending-up" size={20} color={colors.primary} />
            <Text style={[styles.featureText, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>
              AI-powered timeline optimization
            </Text>
          </View>
          <View style={styles.featureItem}>
            <Ionicons name="shield-checkmark" size={20} color={colors.primary} />
            <Text style={[styles.featureText, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>
              Risk assessment & matching
            </Text>
          </View>
          <View style={styles.featureItem}>
            <Ionicons name="analytics" size={20} color={colors.primary} />
            <Text style={[styles.featureText, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>
              Behavioral tracking & insights
            </Text>
          </View>
        </View>
      </View>
    </View>
  );

  if (!isVisible) return null;

  return (
         <BottomSheet
       ref={bottomSheetRef}
       index={0}
       snapPoints={snapPoints}
       enablePanDownToClose
       onClose={handleClose}
       backgroundStyle={[styles.bottomSheetBackground, { backgroundColor: colors.background }]}
       handleIndicatorStyle={[styles.handleIndicator, { backgroundColor: colors.border }]}
     >
      <BottomSheetView style={styles.container}>
        {/* Header */}
        <View style={styles.header}>
          <Text style={[styles.headerTitle, { color: colors.text }]}>Smart Goals</Text>
          <TouchableOpacity onPress={handleClose} style={styles.closeButton}>
            <Ionicons name="close" size={24} color={colors.text} />
          </TouchableOpacity>
        </View>

        {/* Tab Navigation */}
        <View style={styles.tabContainer}>
          <TouchableOpacity
            style={[
              styles.tabButton,
              activeTab === 'insights' && { backgroundColor: colors.primary }
            ]}
            onPress={() => handleTabPress('insights')}
          >
            <Ionicons 
              name="bulb" 
              size={16} 
              color={activeTab === 'insights' ? '#FFFFFF' : colors.text} 
            />
            <Text style={[
              styles.tabText,
              { color: activeTab === 'insights' ? '#FFFFFF' : colors.text }
            ]}>
              Insights
            </Text>
          </TouchableOpacity>
          
          <TouchableOpacity
            style={[
              styles.tabButton,
              activeTab === 'goals' && { backgroundColor: colors.primary }
            ]}
            onPress={() => handleTabPress('goals')}
          >
                         <Ionicons 
               name="flag" 
               size={16} 
               color={activeTab === 'goals' ? '#FFFFFF' : colors.text} 
             />
            <Text style={[
              styles.tabText,
              { color: activeTab === 'goals' ? '#FFFFFF' : colors.text }
            ]}>
              Goals
            </Text>
          </TouchableOpacity>
          
          <TouchableOpacity
            style={[
              styles.tabButton,
              activeTab === 'create' && { backgroundColor: colors.primary }
            ]}
            onPress={() => handleTabPress('create')}
          >
            <Ionicons 
              name="add" 
              size={16} 
              color={activeTab === 'create' ? '#FFFFFF' : colors.text} 
            />
            <Text style={[
              styles.tabText,
              { color: activeTab === 'create' ? '#FFFFFF' : colors.text }
            ]}>
              Create
            </Text>
          </TouchableOpacity>
        </View>

        {/* Tab Content */}
        <BottomSheetScrollView style={styles.tabContentContainer} showsVerticalScrollIndicator={false}>
          {activeTab === 'insights' && renderInsightsTab()}
          {activeTab === 'goals' && renderGoalsTab()}
          {activeTab === 'create' && renderCreateTab()}
        </BottomSheetScrollView>
      </BottomSheetView>
    </BottomSheet>
  );
};

const styles = StyleSheet.create({

  },

FILE: components/UserIncomeSetup.tsx
================================================
import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react';
import {
  View,
  Text,
  StyleSheet,
  TextInput,
  TouchableOpacity,
  Alert,
  Platform,
} from 'react-native';
import { Ionicons } from '@expo/vector-icons';
import { useTheme } from '@/contexts/ThemeContext';
import { supabase } from '@/services/supabase';
import { normalizeFont, spacing } from '@/utils/responsive';
import * as Haptics from 'expo-haptics';

interface UserIncomeSetupProps {
  onComplete: () => void;
  onSkip: () => void;
}

export const UserIncomeSetup: React.FC<UserIncomeSetupProps> = ({ onComplete, onSkip }) => {
  const { colors } = useTheme();
  const [monthlyIncome, setMonthlyIncome] = useState('');
  const [incomeFrequency, setIncomeFrequency] = useState('monthly');
  const [loading, setLoading] = useState(false);

  const frequencyOptions = [
    { value: 'weekly', label: 'Weekly', description: 'Every week' },
    { value: 'biweekly', label: 'Bi-weekly', description: 'Every 2 weeks' },
    { value: 'monthly', label: 'Monthly', description: 'Every month' },
    { value: 'yearly', label: 'Yearly', description: 'Once a year' },
  ];

  const handleHaptic = () => {
    if (Platform.OS !== "web") {
      Haptics.impactAsync(Haptics.ImpactFeedbackStyle.Light);
    }
  };

  const saveIncomeInfo = async () => {
    if (!monthlyIncome || parseFloat(monthlyIncome) <= 0) {
      Alert.alert('Error', 'Please enter a valid monthly income amount');
      return;
    }

    setLoading(true);
    try {
      // Get current authenticated user
      const { data: { user }, error: authError } = await supabase.auth.getUser();
      
      if (authError || !user) {
        throw new Error('User not authenticated');
      }

      // Update user's income information
      const { error } = await supabase
        .from('users')
        .update({
          monthly_income: parseFloat(monthlyIncome),
          income_frequency: incomeFrequency,
          updated_at: new Date().toISOString()
        })
        .eq('id', user.id);

      if (error) {
        throw error;
      }

      handleHaptic();
      Alert.alert('Success', 'Income information saved successfully!', [
        { text: 'OK', onPress: onComplete }
      ]);
    } catch (error) {
      console.error('Error saving income info:', error);
      Alert.alert('Error', 'Failed to save income information. Please try again.');
    } finally {
      setLoading(false);
    }
  };

  const calculateAnnualIncome = () => {
    if (!monthlyIncome) return 0;
    const monthly = parseFloat(monthlyIncome);
    
    switch (incomeFrequency) {
      case 'weekly':
        return monthly * 52;
      case 'biweekly':
        return monthly * 26;
      case 'monthly':
        return monthly * 12;
      case 'yearly':
        return monthly;
      default:
        return monthly * 12;
    }
  };

  return (
    <View style={[styles.container, { backgroundColor: colors.surface }]}>
      <View style={styles.header}>
        <Ionicons name="cash-outline" size={32} color={colors.primary} />
        <Text style={[styles.title, { color: colors.text }]}>Set Up Your Income</Text>
        <Text style={[styles.subtitle, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>
          This helps us provide better financial goal recommendations
        </Text>
      </View>

      <View style={styles.form}>
        <View style={styles.inputGroup}>
          <Text style={[styles.label, { color: colors.text }]}>Monthly Income</Text>
          <View style={[styles.inputContainer, { backgroundColor: colors.background, borderColor: colors.border }]}>
            <Text style={[styles.currencySymbol, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>$</Text>
            <TextInput
              style={[styles.input, { color: colors.text }]}
              placeholder="0.00"
              placeholderTextColor={colors.textSecondary}
              value={monthlyIncome}
              onChangeText={setMonthlyIncome}
              keyboardType="numeric"
              autoFocus
            />
          </View>
        </View>

        <View style={styles.inputGroup}>
          <Text style={[styles.label, { color: colors.text }]}>Income Frequency</Text>
          <View style={styles.frequencyContainer}>
            {frequencyOptions.map((option) => (
              <TouchableOpacity
                key={option.value}
                style={[
                  styles.frequencyOption,
                  { 
                    backgroundColor: incomeFrequency === option.value ? colors.primary : colors.background,
                    borderColor: colors.border
                  }
                ]}
                onPress={() => {
                  handleHaptic();
                  setIncomeFrequency(option.value);
                }}
              >
                <Text style={[
                  styles.frequencyLabel,
                  { color: incomeFrequency === option.value ? '#FFFFFF' : colors.text }
                ]}>
                  {option.label}
                </Text>
                <Text style={[
                  styles.frequencyDescription,
                  { color: incomeFrequency === option.value ? '#FFFFFF' : colors.textSecondary }
                ]}>
                  {option.description}
                </Text>
              </TouchableOpacity>
            ))}
          </View>
        </View>

        {monthlyIncome && (
          <View style={[styles.summary, { backgroundColor: colors.background }]}>
            <Text style={[styles.summaryTitle, { color: colors.text }]}>Income Summary</Text>
            <View style={styles.summaryRow}>
              <Text style={[styles.summaryLabel, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>Annual Income:</Text>
              <Text style={[styles.summaryValue, { color: colors.primary }]}>
                ${calculateAnnualIncome().toLocaleString()}
              </Text>
            </View>
            <View style={styles.summaryRow}>
              <Text style={[styles.summaryLabel, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>Monthly Average:</Text>
              <Text style={[styles.summaryValue, { color: colors.primary }]}>
                ${(calculateAnnualIncome() / 12).toLocaleString()}
              </Text>
            </View>
          </View>
        )}
      </View>

      <View style={styles.actions}>
        <TouchableOpacity
          style={[styles.skipButton, { borderColor: colors.border }]}
          onPress={() => {
            handleHaptic();
            onSkip();
          }}
        >
          <Text style={[styles.skipText, { color: colors.textSecondary }]}>Skip for now</Text>
        </TouchableOpacity>
        
        <TouchableOpacity
          style={[
            styles.saveButton,
            { 
              backgroundColor: monthlyIncome ? colors.primary : colors.border,
              opacity: monthlyIncome ? 1 : 0.5
            }
          ]}
          onPress={saveIncomeInfo}
          disabled={!monthlyIncome || loading}
        >
          {loading ? (
            <Text style={[styles.saveText, { color: '#FFFFFF' }]}>Saving...</Text>
          ) : (
            <Text style={[styles.saveText, { color: '#FFFFFF' }]}>Save & Continue</Text>
          )}
        </TouchableOpacity>
      </View>
    </View>
  );
};

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
  container: {
    padding: spacing.lg,
    borderRadius: 16,
    margin: spacing.lg,
    shadowColor: '#000000',
    shadowOffset: { width: 0, height: 0 },
    shadowOpacity: 0.25,
    shadowRadius: 15,
    elevation: 5,
  },
  header: {
    alignItems: 'center',
    marginBottom: spacing.lg,
  },
  title: {
    fontSize: normalizeFont(24),
    fontFamily: 'Parkinsans-Bold',
    marginTop: spacing.sm,
    marginBottom: spacing.xs,
    textAlign: 'center',
  },
  subtitle: {
    fontSize: normalizeFont(16),
    fontFamily: 'Parkinsans-Regular',
    textAlign: 'center',
    lineHeight: 22,
  },
  form: {
    marginBottom: spacing.lg,
  },
  inputGroup: {
    marginBottom: spacing.md,
  },
  label: {
    fontSize: normalizeFont(16),
    fontFamily: 'Parkinsans-SemiBold',
    marginBottom: spacing.sm,
  },
  inputContainer: {
    flexDirection: 'row',
    alignItems: 'center',
    borderWidth: 1,
    borderRadius: 12,
    paddingHorizontal: spacing.md,
    paddingVertical: spacing.sm,
  },
  currencySymbol: {
    fontSize: normalizeFont(20),
    fontFamily: 'Parkinsans-Bold',
    marginRight: spacing.xs,
  },
  input: {
    flex: 1,
    fontSize: normalizeFont(18),
    fontFamily: 'Parkinsans-Regular',
    paddingVertical: spacing.sm,
  },
  frequencyContainer: {
    flexDirection: 'row',
    flexWrap: 'wrap',
    gap: spacing.sm,
  },
  frequencyOption: {
    flex: 1,
    minWidth: '45%',
    borderWidth: 1,
    borderRadius: 12,
    padding: spacing.md,
    alignItems: 'center',
  },
  frequencyLabel: {
    fontSize: normalizeFont(16),
    fontFamily: 'Parkinsans-SemiBold',
    marginBottom: spacing.xs,
  },
  frequencyDescription: {
    fontSize: normalizeFont(12),
    fontFamily: 'Parkinsans-Regular',
    textAlign: 'center',
  },
  summary: {
    padding: spacing.md,
    borderRadius: 12,
    marginTop: spacing.md,
  },
  summaryTitle: {
    fontSize: normalizeFont(18),
    fontFamily: 'Parkinsans-Bold',
    marginBottom: spacing.sm,
    textAlign: 'center',
  },
  summaryRow: {
    flexDirection: 'row',
    justifyContent: 'space-between',
    alignItems: 'center',
    marginBottom: spacing.xs,
  },
  summaryLabel: {
    fontSize: normalizeFont(14),
    fontFamily: 'Parkinsans-Regular',
  },
  summaryValue: {
    fontSize: normalizeFont(16),
    fontFamily: 'Parkinsans-Bold',
  },
  actions: {
    flexDirection: 'row',
    justifyContent: 'space-between',
    alignItems: 'center',
    gap: spacing.md,
  },
  skipButton: {
    borderWidth: 1,
    borderRadius: 12,
    paddingVertical: spacing.md,
    paddingHorizontal: spacing.lg,
    flex: 1,
    alignItems: 'center',
  },
  skipText: {
    fontSize: normalizeFont(16),
    fontFamily: 'Parkinsans-Regular',
  },
  saveButton: {
    borderRadius: 12,
    paddingVertical: spacing.md,
    paddingHorizontal: spacing.lg,
    flex: 2,
    alignItems: 'center',
  },
  saveText: {
    fontSize: normalizeFont(16),
    fontFamily: 'Parkinsans-SemiBold',
  },
});

================================================
FILE: contexts/ThemeContext.tsx
================================================
import React, { createContext, useContext, useState, useEffect } from 'react';
import { useColorScheme } from 'react-native';
import AsyncStorage from '@react-native-async-storage/async-storage';

// Duolingo-inspired color palette
const lightColors = {
  background: '#F7F9FC',
  surface: '#FFFFFF',
  cardBackground: '#FFFFFF',
  text: '#1F2937',
  textSecondary: '#6B7280',
  buttonBackground: '#FFFFFF',
  buttonText: '#1F2937',
  border: '#E5E7EB',
  shadow: '#000',
  primary: '#10B981',
  secondary: '#1CB0F6',
  
};

const darkColors = {
  background: '#1A1A1A',
  surface: '#2D2D2D',
  cardBackground: '#2D2D2D',
  text: '#FFFFFF',
  textSecondary: '#B0B0B0',
  buttonBackground: '#3A3A3A',
  buttonText: '#FFFFFF',
  border: '#404040',
  shadow: '#000',
  primary: '#10B981',
  secondary: '#1CB0F6',
};

interface ThemeContextType {
  colors: typeof lightColors;
  isDark: boolean;
  toggleTheme: () => void;
}

const ThemeContext = createContext<ThemeContextType | undefined>(undefined);

const THEME_STORAGE_KEY = '@finance_pal_theme_mode';

export const ThemeProvider: React.FC<{ children: React.ReactNode }> = ({ children }) => {
  const systemColorScheme = useColorScheme();
  const [isDark, setIsDark] = useState(false);

  // Load saved theme mode from storage
  useEffect(() => {
    const loadThemeMode = async () => {
      try {
        const savedMode = await AsyncStorage.getItem(THEME_STORAGE_KEY);
        if (savedMode === 'dark') {
          setIsDark(true);
        } else if (savedMode === 'light') {
          setIsDark(false);
        } else {
          // Default to system preference
          setIsDark(systemColorScheme === 'dark');
        }
      } catch (error) {
        console.error('Error loading theme mode:', error);
        setIsDark(systemColorScheme === 'dark');
      }
    };

    loadThemeMode();
  }, [systemColorScheme]);

  // Save theme mode to storage
  const saveThemeMode = async (darkMode: boolean) => {
    try {
      await AsyncStorage.setItem(THEME_STORAGE_KEY, darkMode ? 'dark' : 'light');
    } catch (error) {
      console.error('Error saving theme mode:', error);
    }
  };

  const toggleTheme = () => {
    const newMode = !isDark;
    setIsDark(newMode);
    saveThemeMode(newMode);
  };

  const colors = isDark ? darkColors : lightColors;

  const value: ThemeContextType = {
    colors,
    isDark,
    toggleTheme,
  };

  return (
    <ThemeContext.Provider value={value}>
      {children}
    </ThemeContext.Provider>
  );
};

export const useTheme = (): ThemeContextType => {
  const context = useContext(ThemeContext);
  if (context === undefined) {
    throw new Error('useTheme must be used within a ThemeProvider');
  }
  return context;
};

import { mutation } from "./_generated/server";
import { v } from "convex/values";

export const setupDemo = mutation({
  args: {},
  handler: async (ctx) => {
    // Check if demo user already exists
    const existingUsers = await ctx.db.query("users").take(1);
    if (existingUsers.length > 0) return;

    // Create demo user
    const userId = await ctx.db.insert("users", {
      name: "Alex",
      email: "alex@demo.com",
      avatar: "ðŸ·",
      xp: 150,
      streak: 3,
      lastActiveDate: new Date().toISOString().split('T')[0],
      financialLiteracyLevel: "beginner",
      onboardingCompleted: true,
    });

    // Add some sample expenses
    const expenseCategories = [
      { category: "Food & Dining", amount: 45.50, description: "Lunch at cafe" },
      { category: "Transportation", amount: 12.00, description: "Bus fare" },
      { category: "Shopping", amount: 89.99, description: "New shoes" },
      { category: "Bills & Utilities", amount: 120.00, description: "Electric bill" },
      { category: "Entertainment", amount: 25.00, description: "Movie tickets" },
    ];

    for (const expense of expenseCategories) {
      await ctx.db.insert("expenses", {
        userId,
        amount: expense.amount,
        category: expense.category,
        description: expense.description,
        date: new Date().toISOString().split('T')[0],
        createdAt: new Date().toISOString(),
      });
    }

    // Add a sample goal
    await ctx.db.insert("goals", {
      userId,
      title: "Emergency Fund",
      description: "Save for unexpected expenses",
      targetAmount: 1000,
      currentAmount: 250,
      deadline: new Date(Date.now() + 180 * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000).toISOString().split('T')[0],
      category: "Emergency Fund",
      completed: false,
      createdAt: new Date().toISOString(),
    });

    // Add some achievements
    await ctx.db.insert("achievements", {
      userId,
      type: "lessons",
      title: "First Steps",
      description: "Completed your first lesson!",
      icon: "ðŸŽ‰",
      unlockedAt: new Date().toISOString(),
    });

    return userId;
  },
});

FILE: convex/expenses.ts

import { query, mutation } from "./_generated/server";
import { v } from "convex/values";
import { api } from "./_generated/api";

export const list = query({
  args: {
    userId: v.id("users"),
    startDate: v.optional(v.string()),
    endDate: v.optional(v.string()),
  },
  handler: async (ctx, args) => {
    let query = ctx.db
      .query("expenses")
      .withIndex("by_user", (q) => q.eq("userId", args.userId))
      .order("desc");

    const expenses = await query.collect();

    if (args.startDate && args.endDate) {
      return expenses.filter(expense => 
        expense.date >= args.startDate! && expense.date <= args.endDate!
      );
    }

    return expenses;
  },
});

export const add = mutation({
  args: {
    userId: v.id("users"),
    amount: v.number(),
    category: v.string(),
    description: v.optional(v.string()),
    date: v.optional(v.string()),
  },
  handler: async (ctx, args) => {
    const expenseId = await ctx.db.insert("expenses", {
      userId: args.userId,
      amount: args.amount,
      category: args.category,
      description: args.description,
      date: args.date || new Date().toISOString().split('T')[0],
      createdAt: new Date().toISOString(),
    });

    // Award XP for logging expense
    await ctx.runMutation(api.users.updateXP, {
      userId: args.userId,
      xpToAdd: 10,
    });

    return expenseId;
  },
});

export const getCategoryTotals = query({
  args: {
    userId: v.id("users"),
    startDate: v.optional(v.string()),
    endDate: v.optional(v.string()),
  },
  handler: async (ctx, args) => {
    const expenses = await ctx.runQuery(api.expenses.list, {
      userId: args.userId,
      startDate: args.startDate,
      endDate: args.endDate,
    });

    const categoryTotals: Record<string, number> = {};
    
    expenses.forEach((expense: any) => {
      categoryTotals[expense.category] = (categoryTotals[expense.category] || 0) + expense.amount;
    });

    return Object.entries(categoryTotals).map(([category, total]) => ({
      category,
      total,
    })).sort((a, b) => b.total - a.total);
  },
});

export const getMonthlyTrend = query({
  args: { userId: v.id("users") },
  handler: async (ctx, args) => {
    const expenses = await ctx.runQuery(api.expenses.list, {
      userId: args.userId,
    });

    const monthlyTotals: Record<string, number> = {};
    
    expenses.forEach((expense: any) => {
      const month = expense.date.substring(0, 7); // YYYY-MM
      monthlyTotals[month] = (monthlyTotals[month] || 0) + expense.amount;
    });

    return Object.entries(monthlyTotals)
      .map(([month, total]) => ({ month, total }))
      .sort((a, b) => a.month.localeCompare(b.month))
      .slice(-6); // Last 6 months
  },
});

import { query, mutation } from "./_generated/server";
import { v } from "convex/values";
import { api } from "./_generated/api";

export const list = query({
  args: { userId: v.id("users") },
  handler: async (ctx, args) => {
    return await ctx.db
      .query("goals")
      .withIndex("by_user", (q) => q.eq("userId", args.userId))
      .order("desc")
      .collect();
  },
});

export const create = mutation({
  args: {
    userId: v.id("users"),
    title: v.string(),
    description: v.optional(v.string()),
    targetAmount: v.number(),
    deadline: v.string(),
    category: v.string(),
  },
  handler: async (ctx, args) => {
    const goalId = await ctx.db.insert("goals", {
      userId: args.userId,
      title: args.title,
      description: args.description,
      targetAmount: args.targetAmount,
      currentAmount: 0,
      deadline: args.deadline,
      category: args.category,
      completed: false,
      createdAt: new Date().toISOString(),
    });

    // Award XP for creating a goal
    await ctx.runMutation(api.users.updateXP, {
      userId: args.userId,
      xpToAdd: 25,
    });

    return goalId;
  },
});

export const updateProgress = mutation({
  args: {
    goalId: v.id("goals"),
    amount: v.number(),
  },
  handler: async (ctx, args) => {
    const goal = await ctx.db.get(args.goalId);
    if (!goal) throw new Error("Goal not found");

    const newAmount = Math.max(0, goal.currentAmount + args.amount);
    const isCompleted = newAmount >= goal.targetAmount;

    await ctx.db.patch(args.goalId, {
      currentAmount: newAmount,
      completed: isCompleted,
    });

    // Award XP for goal progress
    let xpToAward = 15;
    if (isCompleted && !goal.completed) {
      xpToAward = 100; // Bonus XP for completing goal
    }

    await ctx.runMutation(api.users.updateXP, {
      userId: goal.userId,
      xpToAdd: xpToAward,
    });

    return { completed: isCompleted, xpEarned: xpToAward };
  },
});

export const delete_ = mutation({
  args: { goalId: v.id("goals") },
  handler: async (ctx, args) => {
    await ctx.db.delete(args.goalId);
  },
});

import { v } from "convex/values";
import { query, mutation } from "./_generated/server";

// Get top 10 users by XP for leaderboard
export const getTopUsers = query({
  args: {},
  handler: async (ctx) => {
    const topUsers = await ctx.db
      .query("leaderboard")
      .withIndex("by_xp")
      .order("desc")
      .take(10);

    // Get user details for each leaderboard entry
    const usersWithDetails = await Promise.all(
      topUsers.map(async (entry) => {
        const user = await ctx.db.get(entry.userId);
        return {
          id: entry.userId,
          name: user?.name || "Unknown User",
          xp: entry.xp,
          rank: entry.rank,
          avatar: user?.avatar || "Ã°Å¸â€˜Â¤",
        };
      })
    );

    return usersWithDetails;
  },
});

// Get user's current rank
export const getUserRank = query({
  args: { userId: v.id("users") },
  handler: async (ctx, args) => {
    const leaderboardEntry = await ctx.db
      .query("leaderboard")
      .withIndex("by_user", args.userId)
      .first();

    if (!leaderboardEntry) {
      // Calculate rank based on XP
      const user = await ctx.db.get(args.userId);
      if (!user) return null;

      const usersWithHigherXp = await ctx.db
        .query("leaderboard")
        .withIndex("by_xp")
        .filter((q) => q.gt(q.field("xp"), user.xp))
        .collect();

      return {
        rank: usersWithHigherXp.length + 1,
        xp: user.xp,
      };
    }

    return {
      rank: leaderboardEntry.rank,
      xp: leaderboardEntry.xp,
    };
  },
});

// Get XP history for a user
export const getXpHistory = query({
  args: { 
    userId: v.id("users"),
    limit: v.optional(v.number()),
    offset: v.optional(v.number())
  },
  handler: async (ctx, args) => {
    const limit = args.limit || 50;
    const offset = args.offset || 0;

    const history = await ctx.db
      .query("xpHistory")
      .withIndex("by_user", args.userId)
      .order("desc")
      .skip(offset)
      .take(limit);

    return history;
  },
});

// Get weekly XP chart data for a user
export const getWeeklyXpChart = query({
  args: { userId: v.id("users") },
  handler: async (ctx, args) => {
    const now = new Date();
    const weekStart = new Date(now);
    weekStart.setDate(now.getDate() - now.getDay()); // Start of week (Sunday)
    weekStart.setHours(0, 0, 0, 0);

    const weekEnd = new Date(weekStart);
    weekEnd.setDate(weekStart.getDate() + 6);
    weekEnd.setHours(23, 59, 59, 999);

    const weekHistory = await ctx.db
      .query("xpHistory")
      .withIndex("by_user", args.userId)
      .filter((q) => 
        q.and(
          q.gte(q.field("date"), weekStart.toISOString()),
          q.lte(q.field("date"), weekEnd.toISOString())
        )
      )
      .collect();

    // Group by day and sum XP
    const dailyXp: { [key: string]: number } = {};
    const days = ['Sun', 'Mon', 'Tue', 'Wed', 'Thu', 'Fri', 'Sat'];
    
    // Initialize all days with 0 XP
    for (let i = 0; i < 7; i++) {
      const date = new Date(weekStart);
      date.setDate(weekStart.getDate() + i);
      const dayKey = days[date.getDay()];
      dailyXp[dayKey] = 0;
    }

    // Sum XP for each day
    weekHistory.forEach(entry => {
      const entryDate = new Date(entry.date);
      const dayKey = days[entryDate.getDay()];
      dailyXp[dayKey] += entry.xp;
    });

    // Convert to array format for chart
    const chartData = days.map(day => ({
      day,
      xp: dailyXp[day] || 0,
    }));

    return chartData;
  },
});

// Add XP history entry
export const addXpHistory = mutation({
  args: {
    userId: v.id("users"),
    xp: v.number(),
    source: v.string(),
    type: v.union(
      v.literal("lesson"),
      v.literal("quiz"),
      v.literal("challenge"),
      v.literal("achievement"),
      v.literal("streak"),
      v.literal("bonus")
    ),
    lessonId: v.optional(v.id("lessons")),
    quizId: v.optional(v.string()),
  },
  handler: async (ctx, args) => {
    const now = new Date().toISOString();
    const today = new Date().toISOString().split('T')[0];

    // Add XP history entry
    await ctx.db.insert("xpHistory", {
      userId: args.userId,
      xp: args.xp,
      source: args.source,
      type: args.type,
      lessonId: args.lessonId,
      quizId: args.quizId,
      date: today,
      createdAt: now,
    });

    // Update user's total XP
    const user = await ctx.db.get(args.userId);
    if (user) {
      await ctx.db.patch(args.userId, {
        xp: user.xp + args.xp,
      });
    }

    // Update leaderboard
    await updateLeaderboard(ctx, args.userId);
  },
});

// Update leaderboard for a user
async function updateLeaderboard(ctx: any, userId: string) {
  const user = await ctx.db.get(userId);
  if (!user) return;

  // Get current leaderboard entry
  const existingEntry = await ctx.db
    .query("leaderboard")
    .withIndex("by_user", userId)
    .first();

  // Calculate new rank
  const usersWithHigherXp = await ctx.db
    .query("leaderboard")
    .withIndex("by_xp")
    .filter((q) => q.gt(q.field("xp"), user.xp))
    .collect();

  const newRank = usersWithHigherXp.length + 1;

  if (existingEntry) {
    // Update existing entry
    await ctx.db.patch(existingEntry._id, {
      xp: user.xp,
      rank: newRank,
      lastUpdated: new Date().toISOString(),
    });
  } else {
    // Create new entry
    await ctx.db.insert("leaderboard", {
      userId,
      xp: user.xp,
      rank: newRank,
      lastUpdated: new Date().toISOString(),
    });
  }

  // Recalculate ranks for all users (this could be optimized)
  await recalculateAllRanks(ctx);
}

// Recalculate all user ranks
async function recalculateAllRanks(ctx: any) {
  const allUsers = await ctx.db
    .query("leaderboard")
    .withIndex("by_xp")
    .order("desc")
    .collect();

  // Update ranks based on XP order
  for (let i = 0; i < allUsers.length; i++) {
    await ctx.db.patch(allUsers[i]._id, {
      rank: i + 1,
      lastUpdated: new Date().toISOString(),
    });
  }
}

// Get leaderboard statistics
export const getLeaderboardStats = query({
  args: {},
  handler: async (ctx) => {
    const totalUsers = await ctx.db.query("leaderboard").collect();
    const totalXp = totalUsers.reduce((sum, user) => sum + user.xp, 0);
    const averageXp = totalUsers.length > 0 ? Math.round(totalXp / totalUsers.length) : 0;

    return {
      totalUsers: totalUsers.length,
      totalXp,
      averageXp,
      topXp: totalUsers.length > 0 ? totalUsers[0].xp : 0,
    };
  },
});

FILE: convex/lessons.ts

import { query, mutation } from "./_generated/server";
import { v } from "convex/values";
import { api } from "./_generated/api";

export const list = query({
  args: {
    userId: v.optional(v.id("users")),
    category: v.optional(v.string()),
  },
  handler: async (ctx, args) => {
    let lessonsQuery = ctx.db.query("lessons");
    
    if (args.category) {
      lessonsQuery = lessonsQuery.withIndex("by_category", (q) => 
        q.eq("category", args.category)
      );
    }
    
    const lessons = await lessonsQuery.order("asc").collect();
    
    if (!args.userId) return lessons;

    // Get user progress for each lesson
    const lessonsWithProgress = await Promise.all(
      lessons.map(async (lesson) => {
        const userLesson = await ctx.db
          .query("userLessons")
          .withIndex("by_user_and_lesson", (q) => 
            q.eq("userId", args.userId!).eq("lessonId", lesson._id)
          )
          .unique();
        
        return {
          ...lesson,
          completed: userLesson?.completed || false,
          score: userLesson?.score,
        };
      })
    );

    return lessonsWithProgress;
  },
});

export const get = query({
  args: { lessonId: v.id("lessons") },
  handler: async (ctx, args) => {
    return await ctx.db.get(args.lessonId);
  },
});

export const completeLesson = mutation({
  args: {
    userId: v.id("users"),
    lessonId: v.id("lessons"),
    score: v.number(),
  },
  handler: async (ctx, args) => {
    const lesson = await ctx.db.get(args.lessonId);
    if (!lesson) throw new Error("Lesson not found");

    // Check if user already completed this lesson
    const existingUserLesson = await ctx.db
      .query("userLessons")
      .withIndex("by_user_and_lesson", (q) => 
        q.eq("userId", args.userId).eq("lessonId", args.lessonId)
      )
      .unique();

    if (existingUserLesson) {
      // Update existing record if score is better
      if (args.score > (existingUserLesson.score || 0)) {
        await ctx.db.patch(existingUserLesson._id, {
          score: args.score,
          completedAt: new Date().toISOString(),
        });
      }
    } else {
      // Create new completion record
      await ctx.db.insert("userLessons", {
        userId: args.userId,
        lessonId: args.lessonId,
        completed: true,
        score: args.score,
        completedAt: new Date().toISOString(),
      });

      // Award XP to user
      await ctx.runMutation(api.users.updateXP, {
        userId: args.userId,
        xpToAdd: lesson.xpReward,
      });

      // Add XP history entry
      await ctx.runMutation(api.leaderboard.addXpHistory, {
        userId: args.userId,
        xp: lesson.xpReward,
        source: `Lesson: ${lesson.title}`,
        type: "lesson",
        lessonId: args.lessonId,
      });
    }

    return { xpEarned: lesson.xpReward };
  },
});
